xt": "68 | 磯風乙改", "links": [{"text": "磯風乙改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%A3%AF%E9%A2%A8%E4%B9%99%E6%94%B9"}], "evidenceKind": "table-row", "context": "初期装備艦は下表の通り。", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "磯風乙改", "shipId": 557, "shipName": "磯風乙改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 557, "canonicalShipName": "磯風乙改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 557, "shipName": "磯風乙改", "apiSortno": 357, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "磯風乙改", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%A3%AF%E9%A2%A8%E4%B9%99%E6%94%B9"}]}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "コモンの朝潮型・陽炎型駆逐艦を改造するとこれを持参してくることが多い。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦は下表の通り。", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "朝潮", "shipId": 95, "shipName": "朝潮", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 95, "canonicalShipName": "朝潮", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 95, "shipName": "朝潮", "apiSortno": 85, "apiAftershipId": 248}}, {"rawName": "陽炎", "shipId": 17, "shipName": "陽炎", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 17, "canonicalShipName": "陽炎", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 17, "shipName": "陽炎", "apiSortno": 91, "apiAftershipId": 225}}]}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2018年8月17日の第二期移行以前は初期実装組の駆逐のほとんどの改装備だったが、移行後及び2020年6月19日のアップデートにて「改」で所持している駆逐艦が大幅に減った。\n朝潮型・陽炎型のコモン艦は1-1でもドロップするので牧場する手間は以前とさほど変わらないが、一期の感覚で間違って改造持参しない艦を育てないように諸提督は気を付けられたし。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦は下表の通り。", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "朝潮", "shipId": 95, "shipName": "朝潮", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 95, "canonicalShipName": "朝潮", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 95, "shipName": "朝潮", "apiSortno": 85, "apiAftershipId": 248}}, {"rawName": "陽炎", "shipId": 17, "shipName": "陽炎", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-na