{"equipmentId": 6, "equipmentName": "20.3cm連装砲", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2", "pageEquipmentId": 6, "sectionHeading": null, "evidenceScope": "page-fallback", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発可", "rawText": "開発可、改修可多くの重巡洋艦の初期装備"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "improvement", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": [], "methods": [{"types": ["development", "ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "開発、初期装備", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "summary-table-cell", "context": "comparison-table"}, {"types": ["ship", "improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "さらに上位の通称3号砲および4号砲もあるが、3号砲は改造艦の初期装備（または改修更新による入手）、4号砲は改修更新による入手であり道のりは長い。", "links": [{"text": "3号砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%283%E5%8F%B7%29%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}, {"text": "4号砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A9%A6%E8%A3%BD20.3cm%284%E5%8F%B7%29%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "nested-page-fallback", "context": "ゲームにおいて"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "改修を進めれば無印→2号砲→3号砲→4号砲まで更新できる。", "links": [{"text": "改修", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0"}, {"text": "青葉", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9D%92%E8%91%89"}, {"text": "衣笠", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A1%A3%E7%AC%A0"}], "evidenceKind": "page-fallback", "context": "ゲームにおいて"}, {"types": ["development", "ship", "improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "2号砲は開発可能であり、3号砲も改造で持参する艦から直接入手、4号砲は直接入手した3号砲からの更新とした方が改修資材の大幅な節約になる。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "nested-page-fallback", "context": "ゲームにおいて"}], "methodCount": 4, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 1, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "fallback", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [], "resolvedQuestKe