 "canonicalShipName": "山城改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 412, "shipName": "山城改二", "apiSortno": 212, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "山城改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%B1%B1%E5%9F%8E%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"rawName": "長門改二", "shipId": 541, "shipName": "長門改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 541, "canonicalShipName": "長門改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 541, "shipName": "長門改二", "apiSortno": 341, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "長門改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%95%B7%E9%96%80%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"rawName": "陸奥改二", "shipId": 573, "shipName": "陸奥改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 573, "canonicalShipName": "陸奥改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 573, "shipName": "陸奥改二", "apiSortno": 373, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "陸奥改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%99%B8%E5%A5%A5%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}]}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "未改造で持参するのは長門型のみ。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "page-fallback", "context": "ゲームにおいて", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "長門", "shipId": 80, "shipName": "長門", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 80, "canonicalShipName": "長門", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 80, "shipName": "長門", "apiSortno": 1, "apiAftershipId": 275}}]}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "長門型からは未改造で1、改造後2と合わせて3つ入手でき、改造Lvも30（Exp43,500）と高くないため牧場による増産も可能。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "page-fallback", "context": "ゲームにおいて", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "長門", "shipId": 80, "shipName": "長門", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 80, "canonicalShipName": "長門", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 80, "shipName": "長門", "apiSortno": 1, "apiAftershipId": 275}}]}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "開発では本装備狙いのレシピではなく、大和砲こと46cm三連装砲の開発のついでに入手する事が多いだろう。", "links": [{"text": "46cm三連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "page-fallback", "context": "ゲームにおいて"}, {"types": ["ranking", "event"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "三連装版の試製41cm三連装砲が2014年夏イベントで、口径が近い16inch三連装砲 Mk.7が2015年12月作戦ランキング報酬として、それぞれ先行実装された。", "links": [{"text": "2014年夏イベント", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/AL%E4%BD%9C%E6%88%A6%EF%BC%8FMI%E4%BD%9C%E6%88%A6"}, {"text": "Iowa", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Iowa"}], "evidenceKind": "page-fallback", "context": "ゲームにおいて"}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "後に試製41cm三連装砲は扶桑改二の初期装備として、16inch三連装砲 Mk.7はIowaの初期装備として、それぞれ本実装された。", "links": [{"text": "Iowa", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Iowa"}], "evidenceKind": "nested-page-fallback", "context": "ゲームにおいて", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "Iowa", "shipId": 440, "shipName": "Iowa", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 440, "canonicalShipName": "Iowa", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 440, "shipName": "Iowa", "apiSortno": 240, "apiAftershipId": 360}, "linkTarget": "Iowa", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Iowa"}, {"rawName": "扶桑改二", "shipId": 411, "shipName": "扶桑改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 411, "canonicalShipName": "扶桑改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 411, "shipName": "扶桑改二", "apiSortno": 211, "apiAftershipId": 0}}]}], "methodCount": 8, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 1, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "fallback", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [80, 81, 149, 150, 152, 209, 210, 211, 212, 275, 276, 411, 412, 440, 541, 573], "resolvedQuestKeys": [], "referenceIssueCount": 1, "referenceSchemaVersion": 2, "rawEvidence": {"cacheKey": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/41cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2.html", "rawPath": ".spider/local/source-cache/wikiwiki.jp/ka