": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "砲系統なので、開発で46cm三連装砲を狙っていると時々出てくる。", "links": [{"text": "46cm三連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "ship", "improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "本装備から15.5cm三連装副砲改二への改修更新を考える場合は、本装備が24本*3必要となる。", "links": [{"text": "15.5cm三連装副砲改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/15.5cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E5%89%AF%E7%A0%B2%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "ship", "improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "上述の開発での副産物だけでは足りない可能性もある。", "links": [{"text": "15.5cm三連装副砲改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/15.5cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E5%89%AF%E7%A0%B2%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "ship", "improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "その場合は41cm連装砲とセット狙いの金剛型の牧場も視野に入るか。", "links": [{"text": "15.5cm三連装副砲改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/15.5cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E5%89%AF%E7%A0%B2%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "金剛", "shipId": 78, "shipName": "金剛", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 78, "canonicalShipName": "金剛", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 78, "shipName": "金剛", "apiSortno": 21, "apiAftershipId": 209}}]}], "methodCount": 7, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 0, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "parsed", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [78, 131, 143, 209, 210, 211, 212], "resolvedQuestKeys": [], "referenceIssueCount": 0, "referenceSchemaVersion": 2, "rawEvidence": {"cacheKey": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/15.5cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E5%89%AF%E7%A0%B2", "rawPath": ".spider/local/source-cache/wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/15.5cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E5%89%AF%E7%A0%B2", "contentSha256": "8ece581821d927f3714e1a4a3930292