{"equipmentId": 13, "equipmentName": "61cm三連装魚雷", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/61cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E9%AD%9A%E9%9B%B7", "pageEquipmentId": 13, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発可", "rawText": "開発可、改修可、入手方法搭載可能艦"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["construction", "development", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": [], "methods": [{"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "開発。空母系あるいはボーキテーブルでなければどの開発からでも出る。", "links": [{"text": "開発", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BA"}, {"text": "九一式徹甲弾", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%8F%E5%BE%B9%E7%94%B2%E5%BC%BE"}, {"text": "発煙装置(煙幕)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%99%BA%E7%85%99%E8%A3%85%E7%BD%AE%28%E7%85%99%E5%B9%95%29"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "水雷系秘書艦よりも砲戦系秘書艦で開発を行うほうが開発成功率が若干高い（4%）。", "links": [{"text": "九一式徹甲弾", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%8F%E5%BE%B9%E7%94%B2%E5%BC%BE"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "各種ホロ大口径主砲や九一式徹甲弾目当ての開発を行うとハズレ枠として開発される事が多い。", "links": [{"text": "九一式徹甲弾", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%8F%E5%BE%B9%E7%94%B2%E5%BC%BE"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "水雷系秘書艦で発煙装置(煙幕)と同時に狙う場合は、鋼材（燃料）テーブルで開発を行う必要がある。", "links": [{"text": "発煙装置(煙幕)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%99%BA%E7%85%99%E8%A3%85%E7%BD%AE%28%E7%85%99%E5%B9%95%29"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ship", "construction"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "初期装備\n最低値建造や1-1でドロップする駆逐艦吹雪、綾波、暁　及び、浦波がドロップ及び改造後の初期装備として持参する。また初春は初期装備としてのみ持参する。", "links": [{"text": "吹雪", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%90%B9%E9%9B%AA"}, {"text": "綾波", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%B6%BE%E6%B3%A2"}, {"text": "暁", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%9A%81"}, {"text": "浦波", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B5%A6%E6%B3%A2"}, {"text": "初春", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%88%9D%E6%98%A5"}, {"text": "61cm三連装(酸素)魚雷", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/61cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%28%E9%85%B8%E7%B4%A0%29%E9%AD%9A%E9%9B%B7"}, {"text": "文月", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%96%87%E6%9C%88"}, {"text": "長月", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%88"}, {"text": "卯月", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%AF%E6%9C%88"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "吹雪", "shipId": 9, "shipName": "吹雪", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 9, "canonicalShipName": "吹雪", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 9, "shipName": "吹雪", "apiSortno": 11, "apiAftershipId": 201}, "linkTarget": "吹雪", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%90%B9%E9%9B%AA"}, {"rawName": "綾波", "shipId": 13, "shipName": "綾波", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 13, "canonicalShipName": "綾波", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 13, "shipName": "綾波", "apiSortno": 17, "apiAftershipId": 207}, "linkTarget": "綾波", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%B6%BE%E6%B3%A2"}, {"rawName": "暁", "shipId": 34, "shipName": "暁", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 34, "canonicalShipName": "暁", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 34, "shipName": "暁", "apiSortno": 71, "apiAftershipId": 234}, "linkTarget": "暁", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%9A%81"}, {"rawName": "浦波", "shipId": 486, "shipName": "浦波", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 4