"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "同じく五十鈴を21号対空電探や改修での対空強化を目当てに牧場していると、いつの間にか溜まっている。", "links": [{"text": "五十鈴", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%81%E9%88%B4"}, {"text": "21号対空電探", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/21%E5%8F%B7%E5%AF%BE%E7%A9%BA%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "五十鈴", "shipId": 22, "shipName": "五十鈴", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 22, "canonicalShipName": "五十鈴", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 22, "shipName": "五十鈴", "apiSortno": 43, "apiAftershipId": 219}, "linkTarget": "五十鈴", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%81%E9%88%B4"}]}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "その他、持参する艦は下記表を参照。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "改修値付きで持参する場合もあるため、牧場対象にする艦の持参形態は確認しておくこと。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "注釈　図:改装設計図、報:戦闘詳報、兵：新型兵装資材", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "table-row", "context": "初期装備として持参する艦娘"}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "1 | 秋月・照月・初月", "links": [{"text": "秋月", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%A7%8B%E6%9C%88"}, {"text": "照月", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%85%A7%E6%9C%88"}, {"text": "初月", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%88%9D%E6%9C%88"}], "evidenceKind": "table-row", "context": "初期装備として持参する艦娘", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "秋月", "shipId": 421, "shipName": "秋月", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 421, "canonicalShipName": "秋月", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 421, "shipName": "秋月", "apiSortno": 221, "apiAftershipId": 330}, "linkTarget": "秋月", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%A7%8B%E6%9C%88"}, {"rawName": "照月", "shipId": 422, "shipName": "照月", "status": "resolv