{"equipmentId": 25, "equipmentName": "零式水上偵察機", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%81%B5%E5%AF%9F%E6%A9%9F", "pageEquipmentId": 25, "sectionHeading": null, "evidenceScope": "page-fallback", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発可", "rawText": "開発可、改修可航空巡洋艦・潜水空母にも搭載可能"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "improvement", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": [], "methods": [{"types": ["development", "ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "開発、初期装備", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "summary-table-cell", "context": "comparison-table"}, {"types": ["development", "ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "多くの重巡、そして水上機母艦が初期装備として持ってくるほか、開発でもガンガン出現する。", "links": [{"text": "零式水上観測機", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E8%A6%B3%E6%B8%AC%E6%A9%9F"}, {"text": "基地航空隊", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%8A"}], "evidenceKind": "page-fallback", "context": "ゲームにおいて"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "2016/03/11に実装された[水上戦闘機]カテゴリの二式水戦改へ改修更新が可能。", "links": [{"text": "二式水戦改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%E6%B0%B4%E6%88%A6%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "強風改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%BC%B7%E9%A2%A8%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "改修工廠について", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%81%B5%E5%AF%9F%E6%A9%9F#renewal"}, {"text": "Ro.44水上戦闘機", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Ro.44%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%88%A6%E9%97%98%E6%A9%9F"}], "evidenceKind": "page-fallback", "context": "ゲームにおいて"}], "methodCount": 3, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 1, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "fallback", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [], "resolvedQuestKeys": [], "referenceIssueCount":