{"equipmentId": 26, "equipmentName": "瑞雲", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%9B%B2", "pageEquipmentId": 26, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発可", "rawText": "開発可、改修可、入手方法搭載可否"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "quest", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": [], "methods": [{"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "初期装備として持参する艦は以下の通り。載せられる娘達が持参するので、赴任初期は問題ないだろう。\n　速吸（Lv1）、伊勢改・日向改・最上改・千歳改・千代田改（Lv10）、扶桑改・山城改（Lv20）、三隈改（Lv30）、鈴谷改・熊野改（Lv35）", "links": [{"text": "速吸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%80%9F%E5%90%B8"}, {"text": "伊勢改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BC%8A%E5%8B%A2%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "日向改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%97%A5%E5%90%91%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "最上改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%9C%80%E4%B8%8A%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "千歳改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%83%E6%AD%B3%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "千代田改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%83%E4%BB%A3%E7%94%B0%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "扶桑改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%89%B6%E6%A1%91%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "山城改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%B1%B1%E5%9F%8E%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "三隈改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B8%89%E9%9A%88%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "鈴谷改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%88%B4%E8%B0%B7%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "熊野改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%86%8A%E9%87%8E%E6%94%B9"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "速吸", "shipId": 460, "shipName": "速吸", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 460, "canonicalShipName": "速吸", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 460, "shipName": "速吸", "apiSortno": 260, "apiAftershipId": 352}, "linkTarget": "速吸", "linkHref": "h