{"equipmentId": 28, "equipmentName": "22号対水上電探", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/22%E5%8F%B7%E5%AF%BE%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2", "pageEquipmentId": 28, "sectionHeading": "入手方法", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発可", "rawText": "開発可、改修可、入手方法海防艦も装備可能「うずしお」での被害を軽減"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["construction", "development", "exchange", "quest", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": ["development", "event", "exchange", "quest"], "methods": [{"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "最低値は鋼150ボ150。開発成功率はホロ電探とほぼ同等(2％)。空母系秘書なら大型電探と同時に狙うことも可能。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "表示上のレアリティは低いが､報告数の多い戦艦秘書・鋼材(燃料)テーブルのレシピで開発できないため、開発成功率が極端に低く見られていた時期があった。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "単独で狙う場合は潜水系鋼材(燃料)テーブルが開発率6%と高い。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "2018/08/17の「艦これ」第二期(HTML5)移行と共に島風が初期装備として持参するようになった。(それまでの61cm四連装魚雷との入れ替わりである)", "links": [{"text": "島風", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%B3%B6%E9%A2%A8"}, {"text": "61cm四連装魚雷", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/61cm%E5%9B%9B%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E9%AD%9A%E9%9B%B7"}, {"text": "沖ノ島海域(2-4)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%97%E8%A5%BF%E8%AB%B8%E5%B3%B6%E6%B5%B7%E5%9F%9F#area4"}, {"text": "キス島沖(3-2)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E6%B5%B7%E5%9F%9F#area2"}, {"text": "北方海域全域(3-4)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E6%B5%B7%E5%9F%9F#area4"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "島風", "shipId": 50, "shipName": "島風", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 50, "canonicalShipName": "島風", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 50, "shipName": "島風", "apiSortno": 10, "apiAftershipId": 229}, "linkTarget": "島風", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%B3%B6%E9%A2%A8"}]}, {"types": ["ship", "quest", "construction"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "沖ノ島海域(2-4)・キス島沖(3-2)・北方海域全域(3-4)でのドロップや、レア駆逐艦レシピ(250/30/200/30)での建造が可能なので、任務消化ついでに拾うことも可能。", "links": [{"text": "沖ノ島海域(2-4)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%97%E8%A5%BF%E8%AB%B8%E5%B3%B6%E6%B5%B7%E5%9F%9F#area4"}, {"text": "キス島沖(3-2)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E6%B5%B7%E5%9F%9F#area2"}, {"text": "北方海域全域(3-4)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E6%B5%B7%E5%9F%9F#area4"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "沖ノ島海域(2-4)・キス島沖(3-2)・北方海域全域(3-4)でのドロップや、レア駆逐艦レシピ(250/30/200/30)での建造が可能なので、任務消化ついでに拾うことも可能。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["ship", "quest", "construction"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "お陰で収集がかなり楽になった。", "links": [{"text": "沖ノ島海域(2-4)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%97%E8%A5%BF%E8%AB%B8%E5%B3%B6%E6%B5%B7%E5%9F%9F#area4"}, {"text": "キス島沖(3-2)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E6%B5%B7%E5%9F%9F#area2"}, {"text": "北方海域全域(3-4)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E6%B5%B7%E5%9F%9F#area4"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "お陰で収集がかなり楽になった。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "第一期と異なり2-4-1ではドロップしない。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備"}, {"types": ["ship"], "avail