{"equipmentId": 36, "equipmentName": "九一式徹甲弾", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%8F%E5%BE%B9%E7%94%B2%E5%BC%BE", "pageEquipmentId": 36, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発可", "rawText": "開発可、改修可、入手方法"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development"], "historicalMethodTypes": [], "methods": [{"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "戦艦の基本装備として重要度が高いが、何気に開発でしか入手できない。開発率は高い方ではないので地道に集めよう。", "links": [{"text": "開発レシピ", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BA%E3%83%AC%E3%82%B7%E3%83%94"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "開発タイプは砲戦系のみ。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "秘書艦（第一艦隊旗艦）が戦艦、重巡および工作艦（明石）で開発できる。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "戦艦は低速戦艦でも高速戦艦でも開発可能だが、航空戦艦(および航空巡洋艦)は空母系のため開発できないことに注意。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "開発最低値は弾30/鋼90。", "links": [{"text": "開発レシピ", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BA%E3%83%AC%E3%82%B7%E3%83%94"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "鋼材テーブルが4%と出やすい、徹甲弾なのに。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "これ単体狙いなら失敗率の高いNelson級が開発資材を節約できる。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "開発レシピを練ろう。", "links": [{"text": "開発レシピ", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BA%E3%83%AC%E3%82%B7%E3%83%94"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}], "methodCount": 8, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 0, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "parsed", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [], "resolvedQuestKeys": [], "referenceIssueCount": 0, "referenceSchemaVersion": 2, "rawEvidence": {"cacheKey": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%8F%E5%BE%B9%E7%94%B2%E5%BC%BE.html", "rawPath": ".spider/local/source-cache/wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%8F%E5%BE%B9%E7%94%B2%E5%BC%BE.html", "contentSha256": "66052cb92bfd309911d3dbcbf4c326ca9304aed7dcafdea04b828ea6a9dd693b", "fetchedAt": 1783531778, "validatedAt": 1783531778, "acquisitionSource": "external-browser-session-crawl"}, "fetchAttempts": [{"candidateSource": "raw-cache", "status": "ok", "url": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%8F%E5%BE%B9%E7%94%B2%E5%BC%BE", "cachePath": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%8F%E5%BE%B9%E7%94%B2%E5%BC%BE.html", "contentSha256": "66052cb92bfd309911d3dbcbf4c326ca9304aed7dcafdea04b828ea6a9dd693b"}]}
