", "apiSortno": 602, "apiAftershipId": 0}}]}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "開発では資源投入量が最少でも出てくる。", "links": [{"text": "開発", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BA"}, {"text": "デイリー開発任務", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Fd3"}, {"text": "失敗ペンギン", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BF%97%E7%A7%B0%E3%83%BB%E3%82%B9%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0%E9%9B%86/%E3%81%AF#penguin"}, {"text": "神風型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%89%A6%E5%A8%98%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%A7%EF%BC%88%E8%89%A6%E7%A8%AE%E5%88%A5%EF%BC%89#Class_Kamikaze"}, {"text": "あきつ丸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E3%81%82%E3%81%8D%E3%81%A4%E4%B8%B8"}, {"text": "神州丸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%A5%9E%E5%B7%9E%E4%B8%B8"}, {"text": "宗谷(特務艦)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%AE%97%E8%B0%B7"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "ボーキサイト>他資材のレシピでは、なぜか開発できない模様。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "何か特別な意味があるのかは不明", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "quest"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "同レシピ等は「開発資材」を貯める目的でデイリー開発任務をわざと失敗したい場合に使用されるため、それを阻害する点で失敗ペンギン以上の怨敵と化すが、", "links": [{"text": "デイリー開発任務", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Fd3"}, {"text": "失敗ペンギン", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BF%97%E7%A7%B0%E3%83%BB%E3%82%B9%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0%E9%9B%86/%E3%81%AF#penguin"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "同レシピ等は「開発資材」を貯める目的でデイリー開発任務をわざと失敗したい場合に使用されるため、それを阻害する点で失敗ペンギン以上の怨敵と化すが、", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["development", "quest"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "最近は改修工廠や任務関連で一定数必要になり、従前に比べ僅かに需要が増している。", "links": [{"text": "デイリー開発任務", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Fd3"}, {"text": "失敗ペンギン", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BF%97%E7%A7%B0%E3%83%BB%E3%82%B9%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0%E9%9B%86/%E3%81%AF#penguin"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "最近は改修工廠や任務関連で一定数必要になり、従前に比べ僅かに需要が増している。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "秘書艦が神風型、陸軍揚陸艦(あきつ丸、神州丸)または宗谷(特務艦)、で開発すると出現率が上がる。", "links": [{"text": "神風型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%89%A6%E5%A8%98%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%A7%EF%BC%88%E8%89%A6%E7%A8%AE%E5%88%A5%EF%BC%89#Class_Kamikaze"}, {"text": "あきつ丸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E3%81%82%E3%81%8D%E3%81%A4%E4%B8%B8"}, {"text": "神州丸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%A5%9E%E5%B7%9E%E4%B8%B8"}, {"text": "宗谷(特務艦)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%AE%97%E8%B0%B7"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}], "methodCount": 7, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 0, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "parsed", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [1, 51, 52, 59, 61, 78, 79, 85, 86, 123, 996, 1002], "resolvedQuestKeys": [], "referenceIssueCount": 2, "referenceSchemaVersion": 2, "rawEvidence": {"cacheKey": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/7.7mm%E6%A9%9F%E9%8A%83", "rawPath": ".spider/local/source-cache/wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/7.7mm%E6%A9%9F%E9%8A%83", "contentSha256": "4f8e62dd17b36feae4d4d526c6d332691053462148b3d3a342d9f313e1909380", "fetchedAt": 1783531784, "validatedAt": 1783531784, "acquisitionSource": "external-browser-session-crawl"}, "fetchAttempts": [{"candidateSource": "raw-cache", "status": "ok", "url": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/7.7mm%E6%A9%9F%E9%8A%83", "cachePath": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/7.7mm%E6%A9%9F%E9%8A%83", "contentSha256": "4f8e62dd17b36feae4d4d526c6d332691053462148b3d3a342d9f313e1909380"}]}
