lability": "historical", "rawText": "(終了済)期間限定任務『賀正！「重巡戦隊」南西諸島へ展開せよ！」』選択報酬(★+8)", "links": [{"text": "賀正！「重巡戦隊」南西諸島へ展開せよ！」", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2021-1"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "本装備が入手できる任務", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "(終了済)期間限定任務『賀正！「重巡戦隊」南西諸島へ展開せよ！」』選択報酬(★+8)", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "(終了済)期間限定任務『【節分任務:恵方】令和六年節分遠征』選択報酬(★+8)", "links": [{"text": "【節分任務:恵方】令和六年節分遠征", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2024-2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "本装備が入手できる任務", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "(終了済)期間限定任務『【節分任務:恵方】令和六年節分遠征』選択報酬(★+8)", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["construction"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "三隈は7-1、4-5、5-2のボスでドロップ、大型建造の最低値等で入手可能の上、Lv30で仕上がるため入手できれば最も効率が良い。", "links": [{"text": "三隈", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B8%89%E9%9A%88"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "利根改二,筑摩改二は改造Lv70と高い上に、設計図を要するため養殖には不向きだが、瑞雲(六三四空)を持ってくる。", "links": [{"text": "利根改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%88%A9%E6%A0%B9%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "筑摩改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%AD%91%E6%91%A9%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "瑞雲(六三四空)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%9B%B2%28%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%9B%E7%A9%BA%29"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "利根改二", "shipId": 188, "shipName": "利根改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 188, "canonicalShipName": "利根改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 188, "shipName": "利根改二", "apiSortno": 188, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "利根改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%88%A9%E6%A0%B9%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"rawName": "筑摩改二", "shipId": 189, "shipName": "筑摩改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 189, "canonicalShipName": "筑摩改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 189, "shipName": "筑摩改二", "apiSortno": 189, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "筑摩改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%AD%91%E6%91%A9%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}]}, {"types": ["development", "improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "20.3cm(2号)連装砲を改修することで、装備更新でも入手できる。", "links": [{"text": "20.3cm(2号)連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%282%E5%8F%B7%29%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "2号砲が開発落ちしたこともあり、比較的現実的な入手経路となったが、2号砲は古鷹型で強い装備ボーナスが発生する。", "links": [{"text": "20.3cm(2号)連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%282%E5%8F%B7%29%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "3号砲の単純な下位互換ではないという点は忘れないようにしたい。", "links": [{"text": "20.3cm(2号)連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%282%E5%8F%B7%29%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "過去には月次作戦報酬として、サービスインからの1年間に10回配布された。", "links": [{"text": "月次作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#PastRewards"}, {"text": "作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#PastRewards"}, {"text": "32号対水上電探", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/32%E5%8F%B7%E5%AF%BE%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2"}, {"text": "烈風", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%83%88%E9%A2%A8"}, {"text": "試製烈風 後期型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A9%A6%E8%A3%BD%E7%83%88%E9%A2%A8%20%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E5%9E%8B"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2013年4～12月作戦報酬、2014年3月作戦報酬で配布。", "links": [{"text": "作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#PastRewards"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "艦これ初のランカー褒賞のひとつだった（その他は、32号対水上電探,烈風（現名称：試製烈風 後期型））。", "links": [{"text": "32号対水上電探", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/32%E5%8F%B7%E5%AF%BE%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2"}, {"text": "烈風", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%83%88%E9%A2%A8"}, {"text": "試製烈風 後期型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A9%A6%E8%A3%BD%E7%83%88%E9%A2%A8%20%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E5%9E%8B"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}], "methodCount": 15, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 0, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "parsed", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [120, 121, 142, 188, 189], "resolvedQuestKeys": [], "referenceIssueCount": 7, "referenceSchemaVersion": 2, "rawEvidence": {"cacheKey": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%283%E5%8F%B7%29%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2", "rawPath": ".spider/local/source-cache/wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%283%E5%8F%B7%29%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2", "contentSha256": "c34b7937c454a4eec153db1202ee9856e2be2fd2ebc998231c228a58c993035a", "fetchedAt": 1783532096, "validatedAt": 1783532096, "acquisitionSource": "external-browser-session-crawl"}, "fetchAttempts": [{"candidateSource": "raw-cache", "status": "ok", "url": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%283%E5%8F%B7%29%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2", "cachePath": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%283%E5%8F%B7%29%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2", "contentSha256": "c34b7937c454a4eec153db1202ee9856e2be2fd2ebc998231c228a58c993035a"}]}
{"equipmentId": 51, "equipmentName": "12cm30連装噴進砲", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12cm30%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E5%99%B4%E9%80%B2%E7%A0%B2", "pageEquipmentId": 51, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発解禁日", "rawText": "開発解禁日:2020年2月7日、改修可、入手方法"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "event", "quest", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": [], "methods": [{"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "2020/2/7アップデートで開発可能になった。", "links": [{"text": "発言", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/p/cushion?to=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKanColle_STAFF%2Fstatus%2F1225769871662706688"}, {"text": "46cm三連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}, {"text": "九一式徹甲弾", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%8F%E5%BE%B9%E7%94%B2%E5%BC%BE"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "戦艦や重巡など砲戦系艦娘では開発報告がなく、他の機銃とは違う。", "links": [{"text": "46cm三連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}, {"text": "九一式徹甲弾", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%8F%E5%BE%B9%E7%94%B2%E5%BC%BE"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "ship"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "改修で必要になるまではそこまで大量に必要になるわけではなく下記のように持参艦も多いため、初心者のうち（少なくとも明石を所持するまで）は狙って開発する意味は薄いか。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "明石", "shipId": 182, "shipName": "明石", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 182, "canonicalShipName": "明石", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 182, "shipName": "明石", "apiSortno": 182, "apiAftershipId": 187}}]}, {"types": ["development", "ship"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "電探開発のついで程度でもよい。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "改造で持ってくる艦がそこそこいるので、気が付くと結構な数が手元にあったりする。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "持参装備での入手"}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "改修での需要が高いため、持参艦の面々を1人ずつ集めた程度では確実に足りなくなる。", "links": [{"text": "雲龍", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B2%E9%BE%8D"}, {"text": "瑞鶴改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%B6%B4%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "翔鶴改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%BF%94%E9%B6%B4%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "千歳航改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%83%E6%AD%B3%E8%88%AA%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "千代田航改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%83%E4%BB%A3%E7%94%B0%E8%88%AA%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "千歳航改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%83%E6%AD%B3%E8%88%AA%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "千代田航改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%83%E4%BB%A3%E7%94%B0%E8%88%AA%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "龍鳳改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%BE%8D%E9%B3%B3%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "天城改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%A4%A9%E5%9F%8E%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "葛城改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%91%9B%E5%9F%8E%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "改装設計図", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0#blueprint"}, {"text": "隼鷹改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9A%BC%E9%B7%B9%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "扶桑改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%89%B6%E6%A1%91%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "神鷹改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%A5%9E%E9%B7%B9%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "試製甲板カタパルト", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0#redprint"}, {"text": "伊勢改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BC%8A%E5%8B%A2%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "戦闘詳報", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E3%82%A2%E3%82%A4%E3%83%86%E3%83%A0#report"}, {"text": "日向改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%97%A5%E5%90%91%E6