e/%E3%82%A2%E3%82%A4%E3%83%86%E3%83%A0#NewModelAerialArmamentMaterials"}], "evidenceKind": "table-row", "context": "初期装備艦は下表の通り。", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "日向改二", "shipId": 554, "shipName": "日向改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 554, "canonicalShipName": "日向改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 554, "shipName": "日向改二", "apiSortno": 354, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "日向改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%97%A5%E5%90%91%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}]}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "千歳と千代田は入手が容易な上にLv50まで上げればLv35時点のものと合わせて2つ入手できるが、1隻をLv50まで上げるより2隻をLv35まで上げた方が必要な経験値は3,500少なくなる（その際の改造による資源消費の合計は、1隻をLv50までが弾800・鋼1220。2隻をLv35までが弾860・鋼1580である）とはいえ低レベル水母と改レベル軽空母では火力やMVP調整に大きな差があるので、Lv35で止めるかLv50まで育てるかはレべリング方法などを踏まえて選ぶと良い。", "links": [{"text": "千歳", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%83%E6%AD%B3"}, {"text": "千代田", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%83%E4%BB%A3%E7%94%B0"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦は下表の通り。", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "千歳", "shipId": 102, "shipName": "千歳", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 102, "canonicalShipName": "千歳", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 102, "shipName": "千歳", "apiSortno": 49, "apiAftershipId": 104}, "linkTarget": "千歳", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%83%E6%AD%B3"}, {"rawName": "千代田", "shipId": 103, "shipName": "千代田", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 103, "canonicalShipName": "千代田", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 103, "shipName": "千代田", "apiSortno": 50, "apiAftershipId": 105}, "linkTarget": "千代田", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%83%E4%BB%A3%E7%94%B0"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "event"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "任務報酬は下記の通り。この他にも期間限定ミニイベントの報酬で入手できた。", "links": [{"text": "松輸送作戦、継続実施せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B113"}, {"text": "戦闘航空母艦一番艦、演習始め！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-C22"}, {"text": "新しき盾", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-C35"}, {"text": "「十八駆」演習！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Cq2"}, {"text": "対空兵装の拡充", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F71"}, {"text": "対空兵装の整備拡充", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Fq6"}, {"text": "工廠稼働！次期作戦準備！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Fq9"}, {"text": "【作戦準備】第二段階任務(対地/対空整備)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B171"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "任務での入手", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "任務報酬は下記の通り。この他にも期間限定ミニイベントの報酬で入手できた。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}], "methodCount": 17, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 0, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "parsed", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [102, 103, 112, 182, 288, 291, 292, 296, 297, 318, 404, 408, 411, 429, 430, 536, 553, 554], "resolvedQuestKeys": [], "referenceIssueCount": 1, "referenceSchemaVersion": 2, "rawEvidence": {"cacheKey": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12cm30%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E5%99%B4%E9%80%B2%E7%A0%B2.html", "rawPath": ".spider/local/source-cache/wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12cm30%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E5%99%B4%E9%80%B2%E7%A0%B2.html", "contentSha256": "7483c53ab16463805f4fc9816ebbf3757cbb3de1b8a60f05c837ce51853216d2", "fetchedAt": 1783532103, "validatedAt": 1783532103, "acquisitionSource": "external-browser-session-crawl"}, "fetchAttempts": [{"candidateSource": "raw-cache", "status": "ok", "url": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12cm30%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E5%99%B4%E9%80%B2%E7%A0%B2", "cachePath": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12cm30%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E5%99%B4%E9%80%B2%E7%A0%B2.html", "contentSha256": "7483c53ab16463805f4fc9816ebbf3757cbb3de1b8a60f05c837ce51853216d2"}]}
