{"equipmentId": 55, "equipmentName": "紫電改二", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%B4%AB%E9%9B%BB%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C", "pageEquipmentId": 55, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発可", "rawText": "開発可、改修可、入手方法"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "exchange", "improvement", "quest", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": [], "methods": [{"types": ["development", "quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "開発、更新任務、複数の出撃系任務の選択報酬で入手できる。", "links": [{"text": "開発", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BA"}, {"text": "Commandant Teste", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Commandant%20Teste"}, {"text": "主力艦上戦闘機の更新", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Fq5"}, {"text": "零式艦戦21型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "零式艦戦52型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A652%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "北方海域戦闘哨戒を実施せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B110"}, {"text": "「伊勢改二」、敵機動部隊を迎撃せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B119"}, {"text": "秋刀魚漁：漁を全力で支援する覚悟です！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2017-5"}, {"text": "迎春！「空母機動部隊」全力出撃！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2018-1"}, {"text": "五周年任務【壱：工廠】", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2018-2"}, {"text": "主計科任務【差し入れ！高級おにぎり】", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2018-3"}, {"text": "【記念任務：拡張作戦】主力オブ主力、決戦ッ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-2304B3"}, {"text": "【年末年始】機動部隊哨戒、南西諸島を防衛せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-2312B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "開発、更新任務、複数の出撃系任務の選択報酬で入手できる。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "開発の場合、空母系旗艦、20/20/10/70の最低値レシピ（ボーキテーブル）で開発できる。", "links": [{"text": "Commandant Teste", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Commandant%20Teste"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "詳細は省くがCommandant Testeを秘書艦にして弾薬20～39までのレシピで開発すると、紫電改二の開発率は変化せずに失敗率だけ上がるため開発資材の節約につながる。", "links": [{"text": "Commandant Teste", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Commandant%20Teste"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "試製烈風 後期型は改造で持参する艦娘がいるが、紫電改二はいまだに誰も持ってこない。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "電改", "shipId": 237, "shipName": "電改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 237, "canonicalShipName": "電改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 237, "shipName": "電改", "apiSortno": 1337, "apiAftershipId": 0}}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "クオータリー任務『主力艦上戦闘機の更新』で3ヶ月ごとに2機入手可能。", "links": [{"text": "主力艦上戦闘機の更新", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Fq5"}, {"text": "零式艦戦21型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "零式艦戦52型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A652%E5%9E%8B"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "クオータリー任務『主力艦上戦闘機の更新』で3ヶ月ごとに2機入手可能。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "更新では、零式艦戦52型から改修値★が引き継がれない。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "更新する機体は改修値の付いていない物を選ぶようにしたい。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "とは言ったものの、52型を改修する利点がほぼないので、むしろ改修値を付けてしまった52型を新たな改修餌としてリサイクルできると見るべきかもしれない", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "図鑑埋めのためにこれを開発しようとして試製烈風 後期型ばかり開発できる物欲センサー発動中という提督もいるようだ。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "逆の提督もいたりして…？", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "任務での入手方法一覧", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "paragraph", "context": "任務での入手方法一覧", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "任務での入手方法一覧", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "クォータリー任務『主力艦上戦闘機の更新』報酬 (x2)", "links": [{"text": "主力艦上戦闘機の更新", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Fq5"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "任務での入手方法一覧", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "クォータリー任務『主力艦上戦闘機の更新』報酬 (x2)", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "任務『北方海域戦闘哨戒を実施せよ！』選択報酬", "links": [{"text": "北方海域戦闘哨戒を実施せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B110"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "任務での入手方法一覧", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "任務『北方海域戦