 "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#PastRewards"}, {"text": "運営ツイート", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/p/cushion?to=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKanColle_STAFF%2Fstatus%2F386777999166554113"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "任務『「十九駆」演習！』選択報酬", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2013年 9月作戦報酬 (1位～200位) (ただし2013年9月作戦の対象は当時の新設サーバのみ、運営ツイート参照)", "links": [{"text": "作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#PastRewards"}, {"text": "運営ツイート", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/p/cushion?to=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKanColle_STAFF%2Fstatus%2F386777999166554113"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2013年 10月作戦報酬 (21位～100位)", "links": [{"text": "作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#PastRewards"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法"}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "綾波以外だと、需要の多い22号対水上電探をセットで持ってくる江風や、陸戦隊の改修に地味に要求される25mm単装機銃をセットで持ってくる狭霧が候補か。\n江風は2-5で、狭霧は7-1でそれぞれドロップするため、たまたま拾ったら利用するといい。最近狭霧は2-2ボスでドロップするようになったため出てきたら育ててもいいだろう。", "links": [{"text": "22号対水上電探", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/22%E5%8F%B7%E5%AF%BE%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2"}, {"text": "江風", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B1%9F%E9%A2%A8%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "陸戦隊", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%A4%A7%E7%99%BA%E5%8B%95%E8%89%87%28%E5%85%AB%E4%B9%9D%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%AD%E6%88%A6%E8%BB%8A%EF%BC%86%E9%99%B8%E6%88%A6%E9%9A%8A%29"}, {"text": "25mm単装機銃", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/25mm%E5%8D%98%E8%A3%85%E6%A9%9F%E9%8A%83"}, {"text": "狭霧", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%8B%AD%E9%9C%A7%E6%94%B9"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦は下表の通り。ドロップ限定艦や高レベル改二艦も多い。\n本装備の共食い改修、C砲やB砲改四等での需要向上を考えると、\n第二期より改でも持参するようになった綾波の育成が、必要Lv・ドロップしやすさの観点では最も平易と言えるだろう。\n特にB砲改四は改修初期段階からB砲を2本ずつ要求してくる。", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "江風", "shipId": 351, "shipName": "江風改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "link-target-more-specific", "evidence": "link-target-authoritative", "canonicalShipId": 351, "canonicalShipName": "江風改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 351, "shipName": "江風改", "apiSortno": 1431, "apiAftershipId": 469}, "linkTarget": "江風改", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B1%9F%E9%A2%A8%E6%94%B9", "linkTextShipId": 459, "linkTextShipName": "江風", "linkTextStart2Ship": {"shipId": 459, "shipName": "江風", "apiSortno": 259, "apiAftershipId": 351}, "shipPageCrossValidation": {"status": "accepted", "reason": "link-page-is-more-specific-than-visible-text", "selectedShip": {"shipId": 351, "shipName": "江風改", "apiSortno": 1431, "apiAftershipId": 469}, "linkTextReference": {"rawName": "江風", "shipId": 459, "shipName": "江風", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 459, "canonicalShipName": "江風", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 459, "shipName": "江風", "apiSortno": 259, "apiAftershipId": 351}}, "linkPageReference": {"rawName": "江風改", "shipId": 351, "shipName": "江風改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-page", "canonicalShipId": 351, "canonicalShipName": "江風改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 351, "shipName": "江風改", "apiSortno": 1431, "apiAftershipId": 469}}, "candidateShips": [{"shipId": 351, "shipName": "江風改", "apiSortno": 1431, "apiAftershipId": 469}, {"shipId": 459, "shipName": "江風", "apiSortno": 259, "apiAftershipId": 351}]}}, {"rawName": "狭霧", "shipId": 391, "shipName": "狭霧改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "link-target-more-specific", "evidence": "link-target-authoritative", "canonicalShipId": 391, "canonicalShipName": "狭霧改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 391, "shipName": "狭霧改", "apiSortno": 1471, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "狭霧改", "linkHref": "https: