1個分の遠征報酬増加能力を持つ唯一の存在で、日々の東京急行系遠征に、それぞれ重宝するだろう。", "links": [{"text": "甲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%94%B2%E6%A8%99%E7%9A%84%20%E7%94%B2%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "標", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%94%B2%E6%A8%99%E7%9A%84%20%E4%B8%99%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "的", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%94%B2%E6%A8%99%E7%9A%84%20%E4%B8%81%E5%9E%8B%E6%94%B9%28%E8%9B%9F%E9%BE%8D%E6%94%B9%29"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "改装時の初期装備", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "阿武隈改二", "shipId": 200, "shipName": "阿武隈改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 200, "canonicalShipName": "阿武隈改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 200, "shipName": "阿武隈改二", "apiSortno": 200, "apiAftershipId": 0}}, {"rawName": "鬼怒改二", "shipId": 487, "shipName": "鬼怒改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 487, "canonicalShipName": "鬼怒改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 487, "shipName": "鬼怒改二", "apiSortno": 287, "apiAftershipId": 0}}]}, {"types": ["ship", "event"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "霰改二は要求レベル63、大潮改二は65、荒潮改二は67と改二勢では低めだが、設計図を使ってまで量産するなら本体の使い道も考えたい。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "改装時の初期装備", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "大潮改二", "shipId": 199, "shipName": "大潮改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 199, "canonicalShipName": "大潮改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 199, "shipName": "大潮改二", "apiSortno": 199, "apiAftershipId": 0}}, {"rawName": "荒潮改二", "shipId": 490, "shipName": "荒潮改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 490, "canonicalShipName": "荒潮改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 490, "shipName": "荒潮改二", "apiSortno": 290, "apiAftershipId": 0}}, {"rawName": "霰改二", "shipId": 198, "shipName": "霰改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 198, "canonicalShipName": "霰改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 198, "shipName": "霰改二", "apiSortno": 198, "apiAftershipId": 0}}]}, {"types": ["ship", "event"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "阿武隈改二・鬼怒改二のような特殊能力は持たされていないが、大発動艇関連搭載可能駆逐艦の中では高火力・生存性も高めなので、イベント時には輸送部隊、対地要員として活躍できる。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "改装時の初期装備", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "阿武隈改二", "shipId": 200, "shipName": "阿武隈改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 200, "canonicalShipName": "阿武隈改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 200, "shipName": "阿武隈改二", "apiSortno": 200, "apiAftershipId": 0}}, {"rawName": "鬼怒改二", "shipId": 487, "shipName": "鬼怒改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 487, "canonicalShipName": "鬼怒改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 487, "shipName": "鬼怒改二", "apiSortno": 287, "apiAftershipId": 0}}]}, {"types": ["quest", "development", "exchange"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "現在、22の任務で入手可能であり、その内3つはクォータリー任務、3つはイヤーリー任務となる。現在は開発可能なので選択報酬は他の物を選んでよいだろう。", "links": [{"text": "強襲上陸作戦用戦力を増強せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B62"}, {"text": "6-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B8%AD%E9%83%A8%E6%B5%B7%E5%9F%9F#area3"}, {"text": "新編「第八駆逐隊」出撃せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B73"}, {"text": "朝潮改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%9C%9D%E6%BD%AE%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "旗艦「由良」、抜錨！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B103"}, {"text": "由良改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%94%B1%E8%89%AF%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "補強増設", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A3%9C%E5%BC%B7%E5%A2%97%E8%A8%AD"}, {"text": "精鋭「第二二駆逐隊」出撃せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B104"}, {"text": "文月改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%96%87%E6%9C%88%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "皐月改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle