elopment"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "開発可能。開発の理論値は鋼材300、よって鋼材maxで開発しないといけない。", "links": [{"text": "開発", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BA"}, {"text": "46cm砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}, {"text": "九一式徹甲弾", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%8F%E5%BE%B9%E7%94%B2%E5%BC%BE"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "ちなみに46cm砲は弾薬テーブルのため複合不可。", "links": [{"text": "46cm砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}, {"text": "九一式徹甲弾", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%8F%E5%BE%B9%E7%94%B2%E5%BC%BE"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "仮に10/300/300/10で開発しても46cm砲は出ない。", "links": [{"text": "46cm砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}, {"text": "九一式徹甲弾", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%8F%E5%BE%B9%E7%94%B2%E5%BC%BE"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "鋼材のみを消費したい場合は有効だが、開発確率は最低(2%)。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "中型の半分ほど…", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "開発ついでに中型バルジができるのはよくあることで、大型1個開発する間に中型が3~5個できていたということも。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "ちなみに中型と同じく開発背景はホロ背景となる。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "任務『水上艦艇装備工廠の整備』選択報酬", "links": [{"text": "水上艦艇装備工廠の整備", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F83"}, {"text": "作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#PastRewards