{"equipmentId": 75, "equipmentName": "ドラム缶(輸送用)", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E3%83%89%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A0%E7%BC%B6%28%E8%BC%B8%E9%80%81%E7%94%A8%29", "pageEquipmentId": 75, "sectionHeading": "ドラム缶の入手方法", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発可", "rawText": "開発可、改修不可、入手方法装備の搭載可否"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "exchange", "quest", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": [], "methods": [{"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "秘書艦が水雷系の場合燃料鋼材テーブル(4%)で出る、最低値の10/10/10/10で開発できる。", "links": [{"text": "10cm連装高角砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/10cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E9%AB%98%E8%A7%92%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "ほかに、10cm連装高角砲レシピ(10/10/30/10)でも出るので、ついでに狙うのも良いだろう。", "links": [{"text": "10cm連装高角砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/10cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E9%AB%98%E8%A7%92%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "潜水系の全テーブルで出る、鋼材・弾薬レシピは開発率が高い(8％)。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "『輸送用ドラム缶の準備』(1回のみ:3個)", "links": [{"text": "輸送用ドラム缶の準備", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F11"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "任務報酬：以下の任務で入手可能。", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "『輸送用ドラム缶の準備』(1回のみ:3個)", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "『資源の再利用』(ウィークリー:1個)", "links": [{"text": "資源の再利用", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Fw1"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "任務報酬：以下の任務で