 "峯雲改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 687, "shipName": "峯雲改", "apiSortno": 1487, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "峯雲改", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%B3%AF%E9%9B%B2%E6%94%B9"}]}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "ただし、いずれも入手機会がレアであり、また運良く邂逅できた場合でも、改造までにそれなりの手間がかかるためお勧めしない。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備"}], "methodCount": 9, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 0, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "parsed", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [323, 687], "resolvedQuestKeys": [], "referenceIssueCount": 4, "referenceSchemaVersion": 2, "rawEvidence": {"cacheKey": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E3%83%89%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A0%E7%BC%B6%28%E8%BC%B8%E9%80%81%E7%94%A8%29.html", "rawPath": ".spider/local/source-cache/wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E3%83%89%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A0%E7%BC%B6%28%E8%BC%B8%E9%80%81%E7%94%A8%29.html", "contentSha256": "2ffd2da58fd6cc4286bf1d838a972b94ed545ed207d363bfd938555788a9796e", "fetchedAt": 1783532709, "validatedAt": 1783532709, "acquisitionSource": "external-browser-session-crawl"}, "fetchAttempts": [{"candidateSource": "raw-cache", "status": "ok", "url": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E3%83%89%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A0%E7%BC%B6%28%E8%BC%B8%E9%80%81%E7%94%A8%29", "cachePath": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E3%83%89%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A0%E7%BC%B6%28%E8%BC%B8%E9%80%81%E7%94%A8%29.html", "contentSha256": "2ffd2da58fd6cc4286bf1d838a972b94ed545ed207d363bfd938555788a9796e"}]}
