 624, "apiAftershipId": 745}, "linkTarget": "涼波改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B6%BC%E6%B3%A2%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}]}, {"types": ["ship", "event"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "このうち秋月型、松型、しまね丸は2025年4月現在通常海域未実装。\n大淀、磯風は1-6でドロップが確認されているが非常に低確率で量産には不向き。\n比較的低改造レベルで持参する艦は、イベント海域や期間限定邂逅で容易なドロップチャンスが設定されたら是非とも確保したい。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦表", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "しまね丸", "shipId": 1003, "shipName": "しまね丸", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 1003, "canonicalShipName": "しまね丸", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 1003, "shipName": "しまね丸", "apiSortno": 603, "apiAftershipId": 1008}}, {"rawName": "大淀", "shipId": 183, "shipName": "大淀", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 183, "canonicalShipName": "大淀", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 183, "shipName": "大淀", "apiSortno": 183, "apiAftershipId": 321}}, {"rawName": "磯風", "shipId": 167, "shipName": "磯風", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 167, "canonicalShipName": "磯風", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 167, "shipName": "磯風", "apiSortno": 167, "apiAftershipId": 320}}, {"rawName": "秋月", "shipId": 421, "shipName": "秋月", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 421, "canonicalShipName": "秋月", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 421, "shipName": "秋月", "apiSortno": 221, "apiAftershipId": 330}}]}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "入手が容易な艦では初春がLv65、浜風が67、吹雪・初霜が70、皐月が75、文月が77、隼鷹が80。", "links": [{"text": "94式高射装置", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/94%E5%BC%8F%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%84%E8%A3%85%E7%BD%AE"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦表", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "初春", "shipId": 38, "shipName": "初春", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 38, "canonicalShipNa