"availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "しいて言うなら吹雪改二は持参装備に同じく改修素材として需要が高い94式高射装置も同時に持ってくるため頭一つ抜けてお勧めである。", "links": [{"text": "94式高射装置", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/94%E5%BC%8F%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%84%E8%A3%85%E7%BD%AE"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦表", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "吹雪改二", "shipId": 426, "shipName": "吹雪改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 426, "canonicalShipName": "吹雪改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 426, "shipName": "吹雪改二", "apiSortno": 226, "apiAftershipId": 1035}}]}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "2026/04/24実装の工廠資源並びに「装備改修度の状態回復」機能実装により★付き装備も改修値を剥がすことで改修餌に使えるようになった。", "links": [{"text": "工廠資源", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E3%82%A2%E3%82%A4%E3%83%86%E3%83%A0#ArsenalResource"}, {"text": "13号対空電探改(後期型)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/13%E5%8F%B7%E5%AF%BE%E7%A9%BA%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2%E6%94%B9%28%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E5%9E%8B%29"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦表"}, {"types": ["ship", "improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "ただし、本装備の更新先の13号対空電探改(後期型)も出撃用や素材としての需要がある。", "links": [{"text": "13号対空電探改(後期型)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/13%E5%8F%B7%E5%AF%BE%E7%A9%BA%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2%E6%94%B9%28%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E5%9E%8B%29"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦表"}, {"types": ["ship", "improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "改修値を剥がす前にそういった運用を行うかどうか事前検討を推奨。", "links": [{"text": "13号対空電探改(後期型)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/13%E5%8F%B7%E5%AF%BE%E7%A9%BA%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2%E6%94%B9%28%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E5%9E%8B%29"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦表"}, {"types": ["ship", "improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "裏を返すと改修値を剥がす気が無くとも★付を貰う価値が高いとも言える。", "links": [{"text": "13号対空電探改(後期型)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/13%E5%8F%B7%E5%AF%BE%E7%A9%BA%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2%E6%94%B9%28%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E5%9E%8B%29"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦表"}, {"types": ["ship", "quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "任務報酬などで★付きの獲得機会があるようであれば、他の選択報酬が魅力的で無ければ本装備を選ぶ理由が出来たとも言える。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦表", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "任務報酬などで★付きの獲得機会があるようであれば、他の選択報酬が魅力的で無ければ本装備を選ぶ理由が出来たとも言える。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["ship", "quest"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "任務『旗艦「霞」北方海域を哨戒せよ！』報酬 (要 霞改二)", "links": [{"text": "旗艦「霞」北方海域を哨戒せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-b58"}, {"text": "霞改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9C%9E%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦表", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "霞改二", "shipId": 464, "shipName": "霞改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 464, "canonicalShipName": "霞改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 464, "shipName": "霞改二", "apiSortno": 264, "apiAftershipId": 470}, "linkTarget": "霞改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9C%9E%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}], "questReferences": [{"rawName": "任務『旗艦「霞」北方海域を哨戒せよ！』報酬 (要 霞改二)", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["ship", "quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "任務 イヤーリー(6月)『AL作戦』選択報酬 (x2、他の選択肢は勲章と補強増設)", "links": [{"text": "AL作戦", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-By9"}, {"text": "勲章", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8B%B2%E7%AB%A0"}, {"text": "補強増設", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A3%9C%E5%BC%B7%E5%A2%97%E8%A8%AD"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦表", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "任務 イヤーリー(6月)『AL作戦』選択報酬 (x2、他の選択肢は勲章と補強増設)", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null