uestName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2026/04/07のアップデートで、本装備が改修可能になった一方で、機種転換任務で改修値を引き継がなくなった*2。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "2026/04/07のアップデートで、本装備が改修可能になった一方で、機種転換任務で改修値を引き継がなくなった*2。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "こちらが本来の仕様通りとの事なので今後同様の任務(F13,F14,F20,F24,F26~F30,Fm1,Fm2等)も修正される可能性がある、未達成の場合は★maxを作成し早めに達成した方が良いだろう。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "F13", "questKey": 614, "questCode": "F13", "questName": "机种转换", "status": "resolved", "evidence": "method-text:quest-code"}, {"rawName": "F14", "questKey": 615, "questCode": "F14", "questName": "机种转换", "status": "resolved", "evidence": "method-text:quest-code"}, {"rawName": "F20", "questKey": 622, "questCode": "F20", "questName": "机种转换", "status": "resolved", "evidence": "method-text:quest-code"}, {"rawName": "F24", "questKey": 627, "questCode": "F24", "questName": "机种转换", "status": "resolved", "evidence": "method-text:quest-code"}, {"rawName": "F26", "questKey": 629, "questCode": "F26", "questName": "“舰战”队再编成", "status": "resolved", "evidence": "method-text:quest-code"}, {"rawName": "F30", "questKey": 633, "questCode": "F30", "questName": "机种转换＆部队再编", "status": "resolved", "evidence": "method-text:quest-code"}, {"rawName": "Fm1", "questKey": 626, "questCode": "Fm1", "questName": "精锐“舰战”队新编成", "status": "resolved", "evidence": "method-text:quest-code"}, {"rawName": "Fm2", "questKey": 628, "questCode": "Fm2", "questName": "机种转换", "status": "resolved", "evidence": "method-text:quest-code"}]}, {"types": ["event"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "「雲龍」は実装当初の2014年夏イベント「AL作戦 / MI作戦」のE-5海域突破報酬以降はイベントドロップのみだったが、", "links": [{"text": "雲龍", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B2%E9%BE%8D"}, 