{"equipmentId": 117, "equipmentName": "試製46cm連装砲", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A9%A6%E8%A3%BD46cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2", "pageEquipmentId": 117, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発解禁日", "rawText": "開発解禁日：2025年10月17日、改修可、入手方法"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "event", "quest"], "historicalMethodTypes": ["development", "ranking"], "methods": [{"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "大和型(大和改二重除く)の鋼材、弾薬テーブルで2%", "links": [{"text": "46cm三連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "鋼材テーブルでも出るため理論値(10/180/230/10)から開発可能。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "大型電探や大型バルジとの同時狙いも可能、両方狙う場合は(10/180/300/250)。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "鋼材テーブルの場合他の大口径主砲は出なくなる。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "弾薬テーブルなら大和型での開発率の上がった46cm三連装砲(10/251/250/10)と同時狙いが可能。", "links": [{"text": "46cm三連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development", "quest"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "2019年2月27日に2つの単発任務の報酬として入手できるようになった。(どちらも選択制だが)", "links": [{"text": "精鋭無比「第一戦隊」まかり通る！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B129"}, {"text": "戦闘詳報", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E3%82%A2%E3%82%A4%E3%83%86%E3%83%A0#report"}, {"text": "試製南山", "href": "htt