{"equipmentId": 120, "equipmentName": "91式高射装置", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/91%E5%BC%8F%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%84%E8%A3%85%E7%BD%AE", "pageEquipmentId": 120, "sectionHeading": "入手方法", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発可", "rawText": "開発可（開発解禁日：2020年3月27日）、改修可、入手方法補強増設に装備可能"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "quest", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": ["event"], "methods": [{"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "初霜改二の初期装備", "links": [{"text": "初霜改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%88%9D%E9%9C%9C%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "初霜改二", "shipId": 419, "shipName": "初霜改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 419, "canonicalShipName": "初霜改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 419, "shipName": "初霜改二", "apiSortno": 219, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "初霜改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%88%9D%E9%9C%9C%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "任務『囮機動部隊支援作戦を実施せよ！』報酬*2", "links": [{"text": "囮機動部隊支援作戦を実施せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-D16"}, {"text": "囮機動部隊支援作戦", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%81%A0%E5%BE%81#id15"}, {"text": "「改装防空重巡」出撃せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B40"}, {"text": "摩耶改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%91%A9%E8%80%B6%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%91%A9%E8%80%B6%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "摩耶", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%91%A9%E8%80%B6"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "任務『囮機動部隊支援作戦を実施せよ！』報酬*2", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "この任務の出現トリガーである任務『「改装防空重巡」出撃せよ！』は摩耶改が必要(改二でなくても可)だが、摩耶はLv18で改装出来るので初心者でも任務達成は容易である。", "links": [{"text": "「改装防空重巡」出撃せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B40"}, {"text": "摩耶改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%91%A9%E8%80%B6%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%91%A9%E8%80%B6%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "摩耶", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%91%A9%E8%80%B6"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "この任務の出現トリガーである任務『「改装防空重巡」出撃せよ！』は摩耶改が必要(改二でなくても可)だが、摩耶はLv18で改装出来るので初心者でも任務達成は容易である。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "2020/03/27でようやく開発が解禁された。さすがに5年4ヶ月は長かった……", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "quest"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "水雷系及び砲戦系秘書艦はボーキサイトテーブル、最低値はボーキサイト【燃10/弾10/鋼10/ボ11】", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "水雷系及び砲戦系秘書艦はボーキサイトテーブル、最低値はボーキサイト【燃10/弾10/鋼10/ボ11】", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["development", "quest"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "空母系秘書艦は鋼材(燃料) or 弾薬テーブル、最低値はそれぞれ鋼材(燃料)【燃10/弾10/鋼10/ボ10】、弾薬【燃10/弾11/鋼10/ボ10】", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "空母系秘書艦は鋼材(燃料) or 弾薬テーブル、最低値はそれぞれ鋼材(燃料)【燃10/弾10/鋼10/ボ10】、弾薬【燃10/弾11/鋼10/ボ10】", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["development", "quest"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "デイリー任務やソナー開発の副産物としても狙える。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "デイリー任務やソナー開発の副産物としても狙える。", "questKey": null, "questCod