C"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備艦", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "雪風改二", "shipId": 656, "shipName": "雪風改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 656, "canonicalShipName": "雪風改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 656, "shipName": "雪風改二", "apiSortno": 456, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "雪風改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%AA%E9%A2%A8%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}]}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "「94式高射装置★max」からの改修更新", "links": [{"text": "94式高射装置★max", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/94%E5%BC%8F%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%84%E8%A3%85%E7%BD%AE"}, {"text": "改修更新", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%A8#id121"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "改修更新"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "「10cm連装高角砲★max」からの改修更新", "links": [{"text": "10cm連装高角砲★max", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/10cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E9%AB%98%E8%A7%92%E7%A0%B2"}, {"text": "改修更新", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%A8#id003"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "改修更新"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2022年 1月作戦報酬 (1位～5位)★+8、(6位～20位)★+7、(21位～100位)★+6、(101位～500位+キリ番＆コメント選抜)★+5", "links": [{"text": "作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#Rewards"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2024年 3月作戦報酬 (1位～5位)★max、(6位～20位)★+9、(21位～100位)★+8、(101位～500位+キリ番＆コメント選抜)★+6", "links": [{"text": "作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#Rewards"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法"}, {"types": ["improvement", "event", "construction"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "入手方法も一筋縄ではいかない。建造不可・通常海域でドロップ不可の秋月型をイベントで入手するか、建造可能だが改二まで改装するのに設計図を3枚消費する雪風改二、あるいは以下の改修更新が必要となる。", "links": [{"text": "雪風改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%AA%E9%A2%A8%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "入手方法の留意点"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "改修工廠で94式高射装置から秋月型(改)または吹雪改二を2番艦にした状態で更新することでも入手可能。", "links": [{"text": "改修工廠", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0"}, {"text": "94式高射装置", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/94%E5%BC%8F%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%84%E8%A3%85%E7%BD%AE"}, {"text": "別の装備", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12.7cm%E9%AB%98%E8%A7%92%E7%A0%B2%EF%BC%8B%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%84%E8%A3%85%E7%BD%AE"}, {"text": "吹雪改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%90%B9%E9%9B%AA%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "初霜改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%88%9D%E9%9C%9C%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "12.7cm連装砲A型改三(戦時改修)＋高射装置", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12.7cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2A%E5%9E%8B%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%89%28%E6%88%A6%E6%99%82%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%29%EF%BC%8B%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%84%E8%A3%85%E7%BD%AE"}, {"text": "任", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F76"}, {"text": "務", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Fq7"}, {"text": "12.7cm連装砲A型改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12.7cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2A%E5%9E%8B%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "更新", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/10cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E9%AB%98%E8%A7%92%E7%A0%B2%E6%94%B9%EF%BC%8B%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%84%E8%A3%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "他", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12.7cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2B%E5%9E%8B%E6%94%B9%E5%9B%9B%28%E6%88%A6%E6%99%82%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%29%EF%BC%8B%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%84%E8%A3%85%E7%BD%AE"}, {"text": "装備", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/10cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E9%AB%98%E8%A7%92%E7%A0%B2%E7%BE%A4%20%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E9%85%8D%E5%82%99"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "入手方法の留意点"}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "吹雪改二が94式を、初霜改二が91式を持参するため一応量産は可能となった。", "links": [{"text": "吹雪改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%90%B9%E9%9B%AA%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "初霜改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%88%9D%E9%9C%9C%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "入手方法の留意点", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "吹雪改二", "shipId": 426, "shipName": "吹雪改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 426, "canonicalShipName": "吹雪改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 426, "shipName": "吹雪改二", "apiSortno": 226, "apiAftershipId": 1035}, "linkTarget": "吹雪改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%90%B9%E9%9B%AA%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"rawName": "初霜改二", "shipId": 419, "shipName": "初霜改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 419, "canonicalShipName": "初霜改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 419, "shipName": "初霜改二", "apiSortno": 219, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "初霜改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%88%9D%E9%9C%9C%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "ただし、改修担当の秋月型がいなければ後述する利点が発揮できない点、94式は「12.7cm連装砲A型改三(戦時改修)＋高射装置」入手任務および12.7cm連装砲A型改二からの更新、そもそも本装備も更新する際に必要になり、更新先含めた他装備の改修にも必要な点から、94式からの更新はよく考えたうえで行ってほしい。", "links": [{"text": "12.7cm連装砲A型改三(戦時改修)＋高射装置", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12.7cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2A%E5%9E%8B%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%89%28%E6%88%A6%E6%99%82%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%29%EF%BC%8B%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%84%E8%A3%85%E7%BD%AE"}, {"text": "任", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F76"}, {"text": "務", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Fq7"}, {"text": "12.7cm連装砲A型改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12.7cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2A%E5%9E%8B%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "更新", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/10cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E9%AB%98%E8%A7%92%E7%A0%B2%E6%94%B9%EF%BC%8B%E9%AB%98%E5%B0%84%E8%A3%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "他", "href": 