t", "canonicalShipId": 649, "canonicalShipName": "高波改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 649, "shipName": "高波改二", "apiSortno": 449, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "高波改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%AB%98%E6%B3%A2%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"rawName": "風雲改", "shipId": 349, "shipName": "風雲改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 349, "canonicalShipName": "風雲改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 349, "shipName": "風雲改", "apiSortno": 1429, "apiAftershipId": 564}, "linkTarget": "風雲改", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%A2%A8%E9%9B%B2%E6%94%B9"}]}, {"types": ["ship", "development", "event"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "鳥海改二は設計図、高波改二は設計図・戦闘詳報・開発資材×20が必要。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "高波改二", "shipId": 649, "shipName": "高波改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 649, "canonicalShipName": "高波改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 649, "shipName": "高波改二", "apiSortno": 449, "apiAftershipId": 0}}, {"rawName": "鳥海改二", "shipId": 427, "shipName": "鳥海改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 427, "canonicalShipName": "鳥海改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 427, "shipName": "鳥海改二", "apiSortno": 227, "apiAftershipId": 0}}]}, {"types": ["ship", "development", "event"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "また高波は6-5ボスマスでのドロップ・風雲は3-5ボスマス、7-2第二ボスマスでのドロップとなる。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "風雲", "shipId": 453, "shipName": "風雲", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 453, "canonicalShipName": "風雲", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 453, "shipName": "風雲", "apiSortno": 253, "apiAftershipId": 349}}, {"rawName": "高波", "shipId": 424, "shipName": "高波", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 424, "canonicalShipName": "高波", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 424, "shipName": "高波", "apiSortno": 224, "apiAftershipId": 345}}]}, {"types": ["ship", "development", "event"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "数が欲しい場合は風雲を狙うか、イベント海域でドロップした風雲・高波を育てるのがよいだろう。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "風雲", "shipId": 453, "shipName": "風雲", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 453, "canonicalShipName": "風雲", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 453, "shipName": "風雲", "apiSortno": 253, "apiAftershipId": 349}}, {"rawName": "高波", "shipId": 424, "shipName": "高波", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 424, "canonicalShipName": "高波", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 424, "shipName": "高波", "apiSortno": 224, "apiAftershipId": 345}}]}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "風雲は3-2ボスマスでドロップするようになった。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "風雲", "shipId": 453, "shipName": "風雲", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 453, "canonicalShipName": "風雲", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 453, "shipName": "風雲", "apiSortno": 253, "apiAftershipId": 349}}]}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "3-2は周回が現実的な海域なので、足りない場合は3-2で風雲を集めて改造するといいだろう。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "初期装備", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "風雲", "shipId": 453, "shipName": "風雲", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 453, "canonicalShipName": "風雲", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 453, "shipName": "風雲", "apiSortno": 253, "apiAftershipId": 349}}]}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "クォータリー『泊地周辺海域の安全確保を徹底せよ！』選択報酬 *2", "links": [{"text": "泊地周辺海域の安全確保を徹底せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Bq8"}, {"text": "熟練搭乗員", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E3%82%A2%E3%82%A4%E3%83%86%E3%83%A0#expert"}, {"text": "洋上補給", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B4%8B%E4%B8%8A%E8%A3%9C%E7%B5%A6"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "任務", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "クォータリー『泊地周辺海域の安全確保を徹底せよ！』選択報酬 *2", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "イヤーリー(6月)『「巡洋艦戦隊」演習！』選択報酬 *3", "links": [{"text": "「巡洋艦戦隊」演習！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Cy5"}, {"text": "22号対水上電探改四", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/22%E5%8F%B7%E5%AF%BE%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2%E6%94%B9%E5%9B%9B"}, {"text": "20.3cm(3号)連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20.3cm%283%E5%8F%B7%29%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "任務", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "イヤーリー(6月)『「巡洋艦戦隊」演習！』選択報酬 *3", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "イヤーリー(10月)『精鋭「第十五駆逐隊」第一小隊演習！』選択報酬 *4", "links": [{"text": "精鋭「第十五駆逐隊」第一小隊演習！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Cy7"}, {"text": "22号対水上電探改四", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/22%E5%8F%B7%E5%AF%BE%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2%E6%94%B9%E5%9B%9B"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "任務", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "イヤーリー(10月)『精鋭「第十五駆逐隊」第一小隊演習！』選択報酬 *4", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "イヤーリー(5月)『精鋭「第十九駆逐隊」、全力出撃！』選択報酬 *5", "links": [{"text": "精鋭「第十九駆逐隊」、全力出撃！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-By12"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "任務", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "イヤーリー(5月)『精鋭「第十九駆逐隊」、全力出撃！』選択報酬 *5", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "イヤーリー(5月)『精鋭「第十九駆逐隊」演習！』選択報酬 *6", "links": [{"text": "精鋭「第十九駆逐隊」演習！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Cy8"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "任務", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "イヤーリー(5月)『精鋭「第十九駆逐隊」演習！』選択報酬 *6", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "イヤーリー(4月)『特型初代「第十一駆逐隊」演習スペシャル！』選択報酬", "links": [{"text": "特型初代「第十一駆逐隊」演習スペシャル！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-Cy10"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "任務", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "イヤーリー(4月)『特型初代「第十一駆逐隊」演習スペシャル！』選択報酬", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "初登場は2015年「1月作戦」のランカー褒賞として配信された(1~100位)。最上級(1~5位)ランカーは2個。", "links": [{"text": "ランカー褒賞", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#PastRewards"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法"}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2015/02/23～03/13の期間限定任務『桃の節句：「菱餅」を沢山集めるのです！』にて、アイテム「菱餅」を10個集めると入手できた。", "links": [{"text": "桃の節句：「菱餅」を沢山集めるのです！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E3%83%89%E3%83%AD%E3%83%83%E3%83%97%E3%82%A4%E3%83%99%E3%83%B3%E3%83%88#Hishimochi"}, {"text": "震電改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9C%87%E9%9B%BB%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "53cm艦首(酸素)魚雷", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/53cm%E8%89%A6%E9%A6%96%28%E9%85%B8%E7%B4%A0%29%E9%AD%9A%E9%9B%B7"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "2015/02/23～03/13の期間限定任務『桃の節句：「菱餅」を沢山集めるのです！』にて、アイテム「菱餅」を10個集めると入手できた。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "余談だが、この10個の任務の任務名、説明文、そして運営Twitterの餅説明がはっちゃけた模様。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "余談だが、この10個の任務の任務名、説明文、そして運営Twitterの餅説明がはっちゃけた模様。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "何ぞや？", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "何ぞや？", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "ちなみに1年以上本実装されていない装備といえばあの震電改や、53cm艦首(酸素)魚雷などがある。", "links": [{"text": "震電改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9C%87%E9%9B%BB%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "53cm艦首(酸素)魚雷", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/53cm%E8%89%A6%E9%A6%96%28%E9%85%B8%E7%B4%A0%29%E9%AD%9A%E9%9B%B7"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "ちなみに1年以上本実装されていない装備といえばあの震電改や、53cm艦首(酸素)魚雷などがある。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "1年どころじゃないとか言わない。", "links": [{"text": "震電改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9C%87%E9%9B%BB%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "53cm艦首(酸素)魚雷", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/53cm%E8%89%A6%E9%A6%96%28%E9%85%B8%E7%B4%A0%29%E9%AD%9A%E9%9B%B7"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "1年どころじゃないとか言わない。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "震電改は遂に10周年記念任務で入手可能に。", "links": [{"text": "震電改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9C%87%E9%9B%BB%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "53cm艦首(酸素)魚雷", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/53cm%E8%89%A6%E9%A6%96%28%E9%85%B8%E7%B4%A0%29%E9%AD%9A%E9%9B%B7"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "震電改は遂に10周年記念任務で入手可能に。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "他にも下記の期間限定任務で入手可能だった。", "links": [{"text": "「西村艦隊」完全編成、出撃準備！』", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2017-6"}, {"text": "主計科任務【高級おにぎりを作る！】", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2018-3"}, {"text": "秋刀魚漁：今秋の「秋刀魚」も上々ね！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2018-4"}, {"text": "続：「鎮守府秋刀魚祭り」発動準備！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2022-7"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "他にも下記の期間限定任務で入手可能だった。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "2017/11/19～12/11　任務『「西村艦隊」完全編成、出撃準備！』選択報酬", "links": [{"text": "「西村艦隊」完全編成、出撃準備！』", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2017-6"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "2017/11/19～12/11　任務『「西村艦隊」完全編成、出撃