ll, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "event"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2015年 夏イベント限定任務『「工廠」”機種転換”』報酬", "links": [{"text": "「工廠」”機種転換”", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2015-2"}, {"text": "E-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8F%8D%E6%92%83%EF%BC%81%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1SN%E4%BD%9C%E6%88%A6#area3"}, {"text": "九七式艦攻(村田隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%94%BB%28%E6%9D%91%E7%94%B0%E9%9A%8A%29"}, {"text": "機種転換任務", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8F%8D%E6%92%83%EF%BC%81%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1SN%E4%BD%9C%E6%88%A6#id-SN08"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "2015年 夏イベント限定任務『「工廠」”機種転換”』報酬", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["event"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "E-3『激突！第二次南太平洋海戦』の共通突破報酬として実装された九七式艦攻(村田隊)を、機種転換することで入手できた。", "links": [{"text": "E-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8F%8D%E6%92%83%EF%BC%81%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1SN%E4%BD%9C%E6%88%A6#area3"}, {"text": "九七式艦攻(村田隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%94%BB%28%E6%9D%91%E7%94%B0%E9%9A%8A%29"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法"}, {"types": ["quest", "event"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "イベント終了メンテナンス実施後には、機種転換任務がイベントと共に消失した。", "links": [{"text": "機種転換任務", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8F%8D%E6%92%83%EF%BC%81%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1SN%E4%BD%9C%E6%88%A6#id-SN08"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "イベント終了メンテナンス実施後には、機種転換任務がイベントと共に消失した。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "event"], "avai