{"equipmentId": 176, "equipmentName": "三式戦 飛燕", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B8%89%E5%BC%8F%E6%88%A6%20%E9%A3%9B%E7%87%95", "pageEquipmentId": 176, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発解禁日", "rawText": "開発解禁日:2026年1月28日、改修可、入手方法基地航空隊にのみ装備可能"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "exchange", "quest"], "historicalMethodTypes": [], "methods": [{"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "開発で入手。2026/01/28アップデートで開発可能に。\n12-B▼装備【開発】更新、さらにもう一つ！\n今日は細かく沢山更新があって、これのご案内もありました！\n「開発」で秘書艦が一部陸軍艦船、またはかの国出身の空母の場合、ちょっと大変ですが、陸軍戦闘機【三式戦 飛燕】の開発も可能になります。\nまた、本日より従来の陸軍艦船に加えて、「山汐丸」もこれらをお手伝いできるようになりました！", "links": [{"text": "12-B▼装備【開発】更新、さらにもう一つ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/p/cushion?to=https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FKanColle_STAFF%2Fstatus%2F2016497968589717648"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "陸軍艦船・Graf Zeppelinが秘書艦で開発率2% (開発レシピ：10/20/10/60)", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["quest"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "任務で入手。", "links": [{"text": "戦闘機隊戦力の拡充", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F80"}, {"text": "烈風 一一型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%83%88%E9%A2%A8%20%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%80%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "Spitfire Mk.I", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Spitfire%20Mk.I"}, {"text": "南西海域「基地航空隊」開設！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B175"}, {"text": "陸軍戦闘機及び海外戦闘機の増備", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F131"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "任務で入手。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "2018年12月7日に単発任務『戦闘機隊戦力の拡充』の選択報酬。", "links": [{"text": "戦闘機隊戦力の拡充", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F80"}, {"text": "烈風 一一型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%83%88%E9%A2%A8%20%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%80%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "Spitfire Mk.I", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Spitfire%20Mk.I"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "2018年12月7日に単発任務『戦闘機隊戦力の拡充』の選択報酬。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "2021年12月28日に単発任務『南西海域「基地航空隊」開設！』の選択報酬。", "links": [{"text": "南西海域「基地航空隊」開設！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B175"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "2021年12月28日に単発任務『南西海域「基地航空隊」開設！』の選択報酬。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "2025年6月27日に単発任務『陸軍戦闘機及び海外戦闘機の増備』の選択報酬。", "links": [{"text": "陸軍戦闘機及び海外戦闘機の増備", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F131"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "2025年6月27日に単発任務『陸軍戦闘機及び海外戦闘機の増備』の選択報酬。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "選択報酬1 【三式戦 飛燕 x2、Spitfire Mk.I x2、二式複戦 屠龍 x2】からの選択。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "選択報酬2 【三式戦 飛燕 x2、Spitfire Mk.I x2、新型航空兵装資材 x1】からの選択。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}], "methodCount": 8, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 0, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "parsed", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [], "resolvedQuestKeys": [], "referenceIssueCount": 4, "referenceSch