{"equipmentId": 178, "equipmentName": "PBY-5A Catalina", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/PBY-5A%20Catalina", "pageEquipmentId": 178, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": false, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発不可", "rawText": "開発不可、改修不可、入手方法秋津洲/改・神威改母・日進改/甲にのみ装備可能"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["event", "exchange", "quest"], "historicalMethodTypes": ["event", "exchange", "quest", "ranking"], "methods": [{"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "2021年現在、常設の入手方法としては、2016年12月9日に追加の任務 (B88)『戦艦戦隊、出撃せよ！』の選択報酬のみ。", "links": [{"text": "戦艦戦隊、出撃せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B88"}, {"text": "二式水戦改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%E6%B0%B4%E6%88%A6%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "二式大艇", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%E5%A4%A7%E8%89%87"}, {"text": "開設！基地航空隊", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E8%A8%AD%EF%BC%81%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%8A"}, {"text": "E-6", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E8%A8%AD%EF%BC%81%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%8A/%E6%8B%A1%E5%BC%B5%E4%BD%9C%E6%88%A6#area6"}, {"text": "【八周年限定】カタリナフェスティバル！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2021-6"}, {"text": "【秋刀魚祭り拡張作戦】北方漁場防衛強化！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-2411B5"}, {"text": "作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#Rewards"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "B88", "questKey": 839, "questCode": "B88", "questName": "战舰战队，出击！", "status": "resolved", "evidence": "method-text:quest-code"}]}, {"types": ["event"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "「二式水戦改」は即戦力として、とても有用な制空用装備だが、（資源コストや手間はかかるが）改修から一応は量産可能。", "links": [{"text": "二式水戦改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%E6%B0%B4%E6%88%A6%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "二式大艇", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%E5%A4%A7%E8%89%87"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["event"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "カタリナの方は主に、イベントの基地航空隊用装備と限られた運用手段で、運用法としても二式大艇に役目を奪われがちだが、", "links": [{"text": "二式水戦改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%E6%B0%B4%E6%88%A6%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "二式大艇", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%E5%A4%A7%E8%89%87"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["event"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "取り逃すと図鑑が埋まらない他、二式大艇がなければ基地隊の行動半径延長手段の一つを失うことになる。", "links": [{"text": "二式水戦改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%E6%B0%B4%E6%88%A6%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "二式大艇", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%E5%A4%A7%E8%89%87"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["event"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2016年 春イベント『開設！基地航空隊』E-6 突破報酬", "links": [{"text": "開設！基地航空隊", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E8%A8%AD%EF%BC%81%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%8A"}, {"text": "E-6", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E8%A8%AD%EF%BC%81%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E9%9A%8A/%E6%8B%A1%E5%BC%B5%E4%BD%9C%E6%88%A6#area6"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法"}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "任務『【八周年限定】カタリナフェスティバル！』選択報酬 (最大2機入手可能)", "links": [{"text": "【八周年限定】カタリナフェスティバル！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99/%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E3%81%AE%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#Q2021-6"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "任務『【八周年限定】カタリナフェスティバル！』選択報酬 (最大2機入手可能)", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "