{"equipmentId": 181, "equipmentName": "零式艦戦32型", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A632%E5%9E%8B", "pageEquipmentId": 181, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発可", "rawText": "開発可、改修可、入手方法"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "event", "quest"], "historicalMethodTypes": [], "methods": [{"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "空母系秘書艦の燃料(鋼材)又はボーキサイトテーブル、水雷系秘書艦のボーキサイトテーブルで開発可能。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "開発理論値の10/20/10/20では弾薬テーブルとなり、どの秘書艦であっても絶対に開発できないため注意が必要。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "最低値レシピは10/20/10/21とみられる", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "開発確率は2％程度と低く、狙い撃ちで開発するのではなく水雷系秘書艦の爆雷・ソナーレシピ、空母系秘書艦のレア艦載機レシピ、電探レシピ(弾薬20以上必須)等でその他装備拡充と並行して確保すると良い。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development", "quest"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "任務『冬季北方海域作戦』報酬 (x2)", "links": [{"text": "冬季北方海域作戦", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-B127"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "任務『冬季北方海域作戦』報酬 (x2)", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["development", "quest"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "任務『空母機動部隊、出撃！敵艦隊を迎撃せよ！』報酬 (x2) イヤーリー(6月) F4F-3、バケツとの選択", "links": [{"text": "空母機動部隊、出撃！敵艦隊を迎撃せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-By8"}, {"text": "F4F-3", "href": "https://