{"equipmentId": 183, "equipmentName": "16inch三連装砲 Mk.7+GFCS", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/16inch%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2%20Mk.7%EF%BC%8BGFCS", "pageEquipmentId": 183, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": false, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発不可", "rawText": "開発不可、改修可"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["construction", "improvement", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": [], "methods": [{"types": ["ship", "improvement", "construction"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "現在の入手方法は改修工廠で16inch三連装砲 Mk.7を更新することのみ。2026年4月7日のメンテで改修元のmk7を持参するIowaが大型建造で入手可能となり理論上量産可になった。", "links": [{"text": "16inch三連装砲 Mk.7", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/16inch%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2%20Mk.7"}, {"text": "Iowa", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Iowa"}, {"text": "41cm連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/41cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}, {"text": "46cm三連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}, {"text": "32号対水上電探", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/32%E5%8F%B7%E5%AF%BE%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2"}, {"text": "22号対水上電探", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/22%E5%8F%B7%E5%AF%BE%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "Iowa", "shipId": 440, "shipName": "Iowa", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 440, "canonicalShipName": "Iowa", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 440, "shipName": "Iowa", "apiSortno": 240, "apiAftershipId": 360}, "linkTarget": "Iowa", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Iowa"}]}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "本装備への更新までには41cm連装砲×18個、46cm三連装砲×12個、32号対水上電探×2個、及び改修資材104個が必要(★+7への改修～更新までを確実化する場合)。", "links": [{"text": "41cm連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kanc