{"equipmentId": 189, "equipmentName": "Re.2005 改", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Re.2005%20%E6%94%B9", "pageEquipmentId": 189, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": false, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発不可", "rawText": "開発不可、改修可、入手方法"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["improvement"], "historicalMethodTypes": ["event"], "methods": [{"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "「Re.2001 CB改★max」からの改修更新", "links": [{"text": "Re.2001 CB改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Re.2001%20CB%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "改修更新", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%A8#id316"}, {"text": "Spitfire Mk.V", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Spitfire%20Mk.V"}, {"text": "Re.2001 OR改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Re.2001%20OR%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "Aquila", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Aquila"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "Re.2001 CB改からの更新ではSpitfire Mk.V1個と新型航空兵装資材3個、熟練搭乗員1個を消費する。", "links": [{"text": "Re.2001 CB改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Re.2001%20CB%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "Spitfire Mk.V", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Spitfire%20Mk.V"}, {"text": "Re.2001 OR改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Re.2001%20OR%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "Aquila", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Aquila"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "また本装備が現状改修不可で対空+11止まりな一方、本装備を作るために基地航空隊で優秀なSpitfire Mk.Vを消費してしまうのも難点。", "links": [{"text": "Spitfire Mk.V", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Spitfire%20Mk.V"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "で~も、あの優秀なスイセーイで改修して、にっくき癇癪女を食って更新できるんだから、それだけの価値はあるわよ。", "links": [{"text": "Spitfire Mk.V", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Spitfire%20Mk.V"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "よしよし☆彡", "links": [{"text": "Spitfire Mk.V", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Spitfire%20Mk.V"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["event"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2016年夏イベント「迎撃！第二次マレー沖海戦」 最終海域E-4 乙作戦以上突破報酬", "links": [{"text": "迎撃！第二次マレー沖海戦", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%BF%8E%E6%92%83%EF%BC%81%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E3%83%9E%E3%83%AC%E3%83%BC%E6%B2%96%E6%B5%B7%E6%88%A6"}, {"text": "E-4", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%BF%8E%E6%92%83%EF%BC%81%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E3%83%9E%E3%83%AC%E3%83%BC%E6%B2%96%E6%B5%B7%E6%88%A6#area4"}], "evidenceKind": "paragraph", "context": "過去の入手方法"}], "methodCount": 6, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 0, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "parsed", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [], "resolvedQuestKeys": [], "referenceIssueCount": 0, "referenceSchemaVersion": 2, "rawEvidence": {"cacheKey": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Re.2005%20%E6%94%B9", "rawPath": ".spider/local/source-cache/wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Re.2005%20%E6%94%B9", "contentSha256": "053f548638b8fd0dfd996e42ba71e44352dd2f2faf14fc45b45c78e57e3847f5", "fetchedAt": 1783535945, "validatedAt": 1783535945, "acquisitionSource": "external-browser-session-crawl"}, "fetchAttempts": [{"candidateSource": "raw-cache", "status": "ok", "url": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Re.2005%20%E6%94%B9", "cachePath": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Re.2005%20%E6%94%B9", "contentSha256": "053f548638b8fd0dfd996e42ba71e44352dd2f2faf14fc45b45c78e57e3847f5"}]}
