{"equipmentId": 201, "equipmentName": "紫電一一型", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%B4%AB%E9%9B%BB%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%80%E5%9E%8B", "pageEquipmentId": 201, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発解禁日", "rawText": "開発解禁日:2022年12月06日、改修可、入手方法基地航空隊にのみ配備可能"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "exchange", "quest"], "historicalMethodTypes": ["ranking"], "methods": [{"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "開発 空母系または藤波改二・早波改二・浜波改二・玉波改二*5旗艦、20/20/10/60が最低値レシピ（ボーキテーブル）*6", "links": [{"text": "開発", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BA"}, {"text": "藤波改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%97%A4%E6%B3%A2%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "早波改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%97%A9%E6%B3%A2%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "浜波改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B5%9C%E6%B3%A2%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "玉波改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%8E%89%E6%B3%A2%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "Commandant Teste", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Commandant%20Teste"}, {"text": "翔鶴改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%BF%94%E9%B6%B4%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "甲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%BF%94%E9%B6%B4%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C%E7%94%B2"}, {"text": "瑞鶴改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%B6%B4%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "甲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%B6%B4%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C%E7%94%B2"}, {"text": "大鳳改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%A4%A7%E9%B3%B3%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "試製烈風 後期型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A9%A6%E8%A3%BD%E7%83%88%E9%A2%A8%20%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E5%9E%8B"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "詳細は省くがCommandant Testeを秘書艦にして弾薬20～39までのレシピで開発すると、紫電一一型の開発率は変化せずに失敗率だけ上がるため開発資材の節約につながる。", "links": [{"text": "Commandant Teste", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Commandant%20Teste"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "藤波改二・早波改二・浜波改二・玉波改二の方が開発率4%と高い。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "空母系でも翔鶴改二/甲・瑞鶴改二/甲・大鳳改を秘書艦にすると開発できないと見られている*7。", "links": [{"text": "翔鶴改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%BF%94%E9%B6%B4%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "甲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%BF%94%E9%B6%B4%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C%E7%94%B2"}, {"text": "瑞鶴改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%B6%B4%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "甲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%B6%B4%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C%E7%94%B2"}, {"text": "大鳳改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%A4%A7%E9%B3%B3%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "試製烈風 後期型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A9%A6%E8%A3%BD%E7%83%88%E9%A2%A8%20%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E5%9E%8B"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "彼女らで開発率が上がる試製烈風 後期型との両面待ちをする際は注意。", "links": [{"text": "翔鶴改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%BF%94%E9%B6%B4%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "甲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%BF%94%E9%B6%B4%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C%E7%94%B2"}, {"text": "瑞鶴改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%B6%B4%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "甲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%91%9E%E9%B6%B4%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C%E7%94%B2"}, {"text": "大鳳改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%A4%A7%E9%B3%B3%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "試製烈風 後期型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E8%A9%A6%E8%A3%BD%E7%83%88%E9%A2%A8%20%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E5%9E%8B"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "任務『運用装備の統合整備』選択報酬 クォータ