{"equipmentId": 215, "equipmentName": "Ro.44水上戦闘機bis", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Ro.44%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%88%A6%E9%97%98%E6%A9%9Fbis", "pageEquipmentId": 215, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": false, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発不可", "rawText": "開発不可、改修可、入手方法"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "event", "improvement", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": [], "methods": [{"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "「Ro.44水上戦闘機★max」からの改修更新で入手可能。", "links": [{"text": "Ro.44水上戦闘機★max", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Ro.44%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%88%A6%E9%97%98%E6%A9%9F"}, {"text": "改修更新", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%A8#id164"}, {"text": "Ro.44水上戦闘機", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Ro.44%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%88%A6%E9%97%98%E6%A9%9F"}, {"text": "Ro.43水偵", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Ro.43%E6%B0%B4%E5%81%B5"}, {"text": "Zara due", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Zara%20due"}, {"text": "Pola改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Pola%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "7-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%97%E8%A5%BF%E6%B5%B7%E5%9F%9F/7-3"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "更新で入手するためには素材のRo.44水上戦闘機に加えて、改修資材54、開発資材132、燃料770、弾薬550、ボーキ2420、瑞雲14、Ro.44水上戦闘機1、が必要となる（★+6→★+7以降を確実化した場合）。", "links": [{"text": "Ro.44水上戦闘機", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Ro.44%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%88%A6%E9%97%98%E6%A9%9F"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "ship", "improvement", "event"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "各所で要求されるRo.44水上戦闘機は開発不可で、新規に手に入れるにはRo.43水偵からの更新もしくはZara dueやPola改の牧場を行うことになる。", "links": [{"text": "Ro.44水上戦闘機", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Ro.44%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%88%A6%E9%97%98%E6%A9%9F"}, {"text": "Ro.43水偵", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Ro.43%E6%B0%B4%E5%81%B5"}, {"text": "Zara due", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Zara%20due"}, {"text": "Pola改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Pola%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "7-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%97%E8%A5%BF%E6%B5%B7%E5%9F%9F/7-3"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "Zara due", "shipId": 496, "shipName": "Zara due", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 496, "canonicalShipName": "Zara due", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 496, "shipName": "Zara due", "apiSortno": 296, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "Zara due", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Zara%20due"}, {"rawName": "Pola改", "shipId": 361, "shipName": "Pola改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 361, "canonicalShipName": "Pola改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 361, "shipName": "Pola改", "apiSortno": 1441, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "Pola改", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Pola%E6%94%B9"}]}, {"types": ["development", "ship", "improvement", "event"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "牧場対象は二人とも7-3にて邂逅可ではあるがイベントや期間限定ドロップのみ、量産や★+6からの改修を視野に入れるとコストは高いと言える。", "links": [{"text": "Ro.44水上戦闘機", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Ro.44%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%88%A6%E9%97%98%E6%A9%9F"}, {"text": "Ro.43水偵", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Ro.43%E6%B0%B4%E5%81%B5"}, {"text": "Zara due", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Zara%20due"}, {"text": "Pola改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Pola%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "7-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%8D%97%E8%A5%BF%E6%B5%B7%E5%9F%9F/7-3"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "Zara due", "shipId": 496, "shipName": "Zara due", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 496, "canonicalShipName": "Zara due", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 496, "shipName": "Zara due", "apiSortno": 296, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "Zara due", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Zara%20due"}, {"rawName": "Pola改", "shipId": 361, "shipName": "Pola改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 361, "canonicalShipName": "Pola改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 361, "shipName": "Pola改", "apiSortno": 1441, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "Pola改", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Pola%E6%94%B9"}]}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "★+5まで改修しないと更新前の★max制空値に届かない。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "更新前のRo.44水戦★maxで制空値を調整していた場合は、最低でも★+5までは一気に改修できる準備をしてから更新しよう。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}], "methodCount": 6, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 0, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "parsed", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [361, 496], "resolvedQuestKeys": [], "referenceIssueCount": 0, "referenceSchemaVersion": 2, "rawEvidence": {"cacheKey": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Ro.44%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%88%A6%E9%97%98%E6%A9%9Fbis", "rawPath": ".spider/local/source-cache/wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Ro.44%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%88%A6%E9%97%98%E6%A9%9Fbis", "contentSha256": "5614633e77a59ca601f59ead4a3772c231bd829cc9f734fbf8ed1c5d2a6db36d", "fetchedAt": 1783536560, "validatedAt": 1783536560, "acquisitionSource": "external-browser-session-crawl"}, "fetchAttempts": [{"candidateSource": "raw-cache", "status": "ok", "url": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Ro.44%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%88%A6%E9%97%98%E6%A9%9Fbis", "cachePath": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Ro.44%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E6%88%A6%E9%97%98%E6%A9%9Fbis", "contentSha256": "5614633e77a59ca601f59ead4a3772c231bd829cc9f734fbf8ed1c5d2a6db36d"}]}
