{"equipmentId": 250, "equipmentName": "Spitfire Mk.I", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Spitfire%20Mk.I", "pageEquipmentId": 250, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発可", "rawText": "開発可(特殊)、改修可、入手方法基地航空隊にのみ装備可能"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "exchange", "quest"], "historicalMethodTypes": ["development", "event"], "methods": [{"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "秘書艦Warspite・Nelson・Rodneyでのみ開発可能。開発理論値は10/20/10/40で開発成功率は6％。", "links": [{"text": "Warspite", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Warspite"}, {"text": "Nelson", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Nelson"}, {"text": "Rodney", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Rodney"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "開発はボーキサイトテーブル限定で、普段戦艦（砲戦系秘書）で開発する大型電探やバルジとの同時狙いは不可能。大口径主砲や22,33号等の一部の小型電探は開発可能だが極めて効率が悪い。\n専用レシピで開発するのが良いだろう。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "開発"}, {"types": ["development", "quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "任務『戦闘機隊戦力の拡充』選択報酬", "links": [{"text": "戦闘機隊戦力の拡充", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F80"}, {"text": "烈風 一一型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%83%88%E9%A2%A8%20%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%80%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "三式戦 飛燕", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B8%89%E5%BC%8F%E6%88%A6%20%E9%A3%9B%E7%87%95"}, {"text": "Spitfire Mk.I", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Spitfire%20Mk.I"}, {"text": "紫電二一型 紫電改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%B4%AB%E9%9B%BB%E4%BA%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%9E%8B%20%E7%B4%AB%E9%9B%BB%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "二式複戦 屠龍", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%E8%A4%87%E6%88%A6%20%E5%B1%A0%E9%BE%8D"}, {"text": "西方再打通！欧州救援作戦", "href": "htt