{"equipmentId": 266, "equipmentName": "12.7cm連装砲C型改二", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12.7cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2C%E5%9E%8B%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C", "pageEquipmentId": 266, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": false, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発不可", "rawText": "開発不可、改修可、入手方法"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["construction", "development", "improvement", "quest", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": ["event", "ranking"], "methods": [{"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "前述の通り改造時に設計図や戦闘詳報等の特別なアイテムを必要としない満潮改二が持参する。\n改造に要するレベルは高いものの低コストで量産できるため、労力を許容できるなら有力な候補となる。", "links": [{"text": "満潮改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%BA%80%E6%BD%AE%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "満潮改二", "shipId": 489, "shipName": "満潮改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 489, "canonicalShipName": "満潮改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 489, "shipName": "満潮改二", "apiSortno": 289, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "満潮改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%BA%80%E6%BD%AE%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}]}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "12.7cm連装砲B型改二からの更新でも入手可能で、装備自体も改修可能。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ship", "improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "ただし改修更新を用いた量産は大量のネジを消費するため、満潮改二の牧場が許容できるなら労力はともかくネジの面ではコストパフォーマンスに優れる。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "満潮改二", "shipId": 489, "shipName": "満潮改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 489, "canonicalShipName": "満潮改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 489, "shipName": "満潮改二", "apiSortno": 289, "apiAftershipId": 0}}]}, {"types": ["ship", "improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "牧場を行いたくない、ネジ消費を度外視する、レベリングを待たずに手に入れたいなどという場合を除き余り推奨はされないだろう。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement", "ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "更新入手には12.7cm連装砲B型改二が最低5つ必要な為、春雨改等の比較的低レベル改造でB型を持参する艦が複数集まった場合に、廃棄か改修かを検討する程度で十分だろう。\n第二期より綾波改が持参するようになった為、更新入手のハードルは大幅に下がった。", "links": [{"text": "春雨改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%98%A5%E9%9B%A8%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "綾波改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%B6%BE%E6%B3%A2%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "満潮改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%BA%80%E6%BD%AE%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "12.7cm連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12.7cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "B型改二からの更新について", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "春雨改", "shipId": 323, "shipName": "春雨改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 323, "canonicalShipName": "春雨改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 323, "shipName": "春雨改", "apiSortno": 1416, "apiAftershipId": 975}, "linkTarget": "春雨改", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%98%A5%E9%9B%A8%E6%94%B9"}, {"rawName": "綾波改", "shipId": 207, "shipName": "綾波改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 207, "canonicalShipName": "綾波改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 207, "shipName": "綾波改", "apiSortno": 1307, "apiAftershipId": 195}, "linkTarget": "綾波改", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%B6%BE%E6%B3%A2%E6%94%B9"}, {"rawName": "満潮改二", "shipId": 489, "shipName": "満潮改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 489, "canonicalShipName": "満潮改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 489, "shipName": "満潮改二", "apiSortno": 289, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "満潮改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%BA%80%E6%BD%AE%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}]}, {"types": ["improvement", "ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "必要経験値を比較すると、綾波改を5隻牧場した場合は19,000*5=95,000、満潮改二牧場で直接入手する場合は343,400。", "links": [{"text": "満潮改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%BA%80%E6%BD%AE%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "B型改二からの更新について", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "満潮改二", "shipId": 489, "shipName": "満潮改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 489, "canonicalShipName": "満潮改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 489, "shipName": "満潮改二", "apiSortno": 289, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "満潮改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%BA%80%E6%BD%AE%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"rawName": "綾波改", "shipId": 207, "shipName": "綾波改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 207, "canonicalShipName": "綾波改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 207, "shipName": "綾波改", "apiSortno": 1307, "apiAftershipId": 195}}]}, {"types": ["improvement", "ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "B型改二からの更新には更に改修費用が上乗せされる。", "links": [{"text": "満潮改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%BA%80%E6%BD%AE%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "B型改二からの更新について", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "満潮改二", "shipId": 489, "shipName": "満潮改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 489, "canonicalShipName": "満潮改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 489, "shipName": "満潮改二", "apiSortno": 289, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "満潮改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%BA%80%E6%BD%AE%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}]}, {"types": ["improvement", "ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "綾波牧場をしない場合は12.7cm連装砲から改修を繰り返す必要があり、共食い改修も含まれる為、資材はともかく準備時間はかかる。", "links": [{"text": "12.7cm連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12.7cm%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "B型改二からの更新について", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "綾波", "shipId": 13, "shipName": "綾波", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "method-text", "canonicalShipId": 13, "canonicalShipName": "綾波", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 13, "shipName": "綾波", "apiSortno": 17, "apiAftershipId": 207}}]}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "参考値", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "B型改二からの更新について"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "満潮改二：EXP=343,400", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "B型改二からの更新について"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "霰改二　：EXP=203,400、設計図1=勲章4=ネジ16", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "B型改二からの更新について"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "Ｂ型更新：綾波改5(EXP=95,000)、ネジ35(前半2*6回+後半4(確実化)*4回+更新7(確実化))", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "B型改二からの更新について"}, {"types": ["ship", "development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "63 | 霰改二 | 203,400 | 設計図", "links": [{"text": "霰改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9C%B0%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}], "evidenceKind": "table-row", "context": "陽炎改二 | 設計図、開発資材x20", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "霰改二", "shipId": 198, "shipName": "霰改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 198, "canonicalShipName": "霰改二", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 198, "shipName": "霰改二", "apiSortno": 198, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "霰改二", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9C%B0%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}]}, {"types": ["ship", "development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "70 | 村雨改二 | 265,000 | 戦闘詳報", "links": [{"text": "村雨改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%9D%91%E9%9B%A8%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}], "evidenceKind": "table-row", "context": "陽炎改二 | 設計図、開発資材x20", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "村雨改二", "shipId": 498, "shipName": "村雨改二", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 498, "canonica