{"equipmentId": 298, "equipmentName": "16inch Mk.I三連装砲", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/16inch%20Mk.I%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2", "pageEquipmentId": 298, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発解禁日", "rawText": "開発解禁日:2022年12月6日、改修可、入手方法"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": ["ranking"], "methods": [{"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "Nelson・Rodneyの初期装備", "links": [{"text": "Nelson", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Nelson"}, {"text": "Rodney", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Rodney"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "Nelson", "shipId": 571, "shipName": "Nelson", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 571, "canonicalShipName": "Nelson", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 571, "shipName": "Nelson", "apiSortno": 371, "apiAftershipId": 576}, "linkTarget": "Nelson", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Nelson"}, {"rawName": "Rodney", "shipId": 572, "shipName": "Rodney", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 572, "canonicalShipName": "Rodney", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 572, "shipName": "Rodney", "apiSortno": 372, "apiAftershipId": 577}, "linkTarget": "Rodney", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Rodney"}]}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "2022年12月6日 開発可能となり、同時に英国系大口径主砲の改修必要装備に指定される。", "links": [{"text": "開発", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BA"}, {"text": "20連装7inch UP Rocket Launchers", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%857inch%20UP%20Rocket%20Launchers"}, {"text": "46cm三連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "ネルソンorロドニー旗艦、開発レシピ(10/211/210/10)で開発可能(開発率8%)。", "links": [{"text": "20連装7inch UP Rocket Launchers", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%857inch%20UP%20Rocket%20Launchers"}, {"text": "46cm三連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "弾薬150でも開発可能であるが、弾薬テーブルでないと開発率が下がるため211まで盛ったほうがよい。", "links": [{"text": "20連装7inch UP Rocket Launchers", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%857inch%20UP%20Rocket%20Launchers"}, {"text": "46cm三連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "投入資材(10/211/210/40)で20連装7inch UP Rocket Launchers(開発率6%)が追加される。", "links": [{"text": "20連装7inch UP Rocket Launchers", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/20%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%857inch%20UP%20Rocket%20Launchers"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "投入資材(10/251/250/40)で更に46cm三連装砲(開発率2%)も追加される。", "links": [{"text": "46cm三連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "ただしネルソン級が旗艦のときは通常時(開発率4%、大和型戦艦旗艦 推定6%)より開発率が下がる点に留意。", "links": [{"text": "46cm三連装砲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/46cm%E4%B8%89%E9%80%A3%E8%A3%85%E7%A0%B2"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2018年6月作戦報酬", "links": [{"text": "作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#PastRewards"}], "evidenceKind": "paragraph", "context": "過去の入手方法"}], "methodCount": 8, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 0, "accepted": true, "cove