{"equipmentId": 420, "equipmentName": "SB2C-3", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/SB2C-3", "pageEquipmentId": 420, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": false, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発不可", "rawText": "開発不可、改修可、入手方法"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development", "exchange", "improvement", "quest", "ship"], "historicalMethodTypes": ["ranking"], "methods": [{"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "「SBD-5★max」から改修更新", "links": [{"text": "SBD-5★max", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/SBD-5"}, {"text": "改修更新", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%A8#id419"}, {"text": "作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#PastRewards"}, {"text": "作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#Rewards"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2021年 05月作戦報酬 (1位～5位)★+5、(6位～20位)★+3、(21位～100位)★+3、(101位～500位)★無し", "links": [{"text": "作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#PastRewards"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2021年 10月作戦報酬 (21位～100位)★+3", "links": [{"text": "作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#PastRewards"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法"}, {"types": ["ranking"], "availability": "historical", "rawText": "2022年 09月作戦報酬 (21位～100位)★+4", "links": [{"text": "作戦報酬", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E5%80%89%E5%BA%AB#Rewards"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "過去の入手方法"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "SBDは開発可能。", "links": [{"text": "SBD", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/SBD"}, {"text": "空母機動部隊、出撃！敵艦隊を迎撃せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-By8"}, {"text": "二二型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B9%9D%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E7%88%86%E4%BA%8C%E4%BA%8C%E5%9E%8B"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "改修素材の入手について"}, {"types": ["quest", "exchange"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "イヤーリー(6月) 任務『空母機動部隊、出撃！敵艦隊を迎撃せよ！』の選択報酬として一応SBDを各２機ずつ入手できる。", "links": [{"text": "空母機動部隊、出撃！敵艦隊を迎撃せよ！", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-By8"}, {"text": "二二型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B9%9D%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E7%88%86%E4%BA%8C%E4%BA%8C%E5%9E%8B"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "改修素材の入手について", "questReferences": [{"rawName": "イヤーリー(6月) 任務『空母機動部隊、出撃！敵艦隊を迎撃せよ！』の選択報酬として一応SBDを各２機ずつ入手できる。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}]}, {"types": ["improvement", "development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "開発可能なSBDから改修更新で本装備を作るには、下記の資材・装備が必要となる。\n開発資材107個と改修資材78個*5(★+6以降を確実化する場合)*6、新型航空兵装資材x3、熟練搭乗員x1\n九九式艦爆x26、SBDx4、F4F-4x1、F6F-3x1", "links": [{"text": "SBD", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/SBD"}, {"text": "九九式艦爆", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B9%9D%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E7%88%86"}, {"text": "F4F-4", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F4F-4"}, {"text": "F4F-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F4F-3"}, {"text": "九六式艦戦", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E5%85%AD%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A6"}, {"text": "12.7mm単装機銃", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12.7mm%E5%8D%98%E8%A3%85%E6%A9%9F%E9%8A%83"}, {"text": "零式艦戦21型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "32型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A632%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "52型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A652%E5%9E%8B"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "SBDから改修更新する場合"}, {"types": ["improvement", "development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "また、改修で消費するF4F-4とF6F-3を、開発可能なF4F-3からそれぞれ1つずつ用意する場合は追加として、", "links": [{"text": "F4F-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F4F-3"}, {"text": "九六式艦戦", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E5%85%AD%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A6"}, {"text": "12.7mm単装機銃", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12.7mm%E5%8D%98%E8%A3%85%E6%A9%9F%E9%8A%83"}, {"text": "零式艦戦21型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "32型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A632%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "52型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A652%E5%9E%8B"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "SBDから改修更新する場合"}, {"types": ["improvement", "development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "開発資材154個と改修資材117個*7(★+6以降を確実化する場合)*8F6F-3を作る方が重い…", "links": [{"text": "F4F-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F4F-3"}, {"text": "九六式艦戦", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E5%85%AD%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A6"}, {"text": "12.7mm単装機銃", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12.7mm%E5%8D%98%E8%A3%85%E6%A9%9F%E9%8A%83"}, {"text": "零式艦戦21型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "32型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A632%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "52型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A652%E5%9E%8B"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "SBDから改修更新する場合"}, {"types": ["improvement", "development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "九六式艦戦x8、12.7mm単装機銃x4、零式艦戦21型x6、32型x4、52型x2が必要。", "links": [{"text": "F4F-3", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F4F-3"}, {"text": "九六式艦戦", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E5%85%AD%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A6"}, {"text": "12.7mm単装機銃", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/12.7mm%E5%8D%98%E8%A3%85%E6%A9%9F%E9%8A%83"}, {"text": "零式艦戦21型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "32型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A632%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "52型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A652%E5%9E%8B"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "SBDから改修更新する場合"}, {"types": ["improvement", "development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "つまり、一からこの装備を作ろうとすると開発資材261個と改修資材195個も必要になる(★+6以降を確実化する場合)*9", "links": [{"text": "九九式艦爆(江草隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B9%9D%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E7%88%86%28%E6%B1%9F%E8%8D%89%E9%9A%8A%29"}, {"text": "彗星(江草隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%BD%97%E6%98%9F%28%E6%B1%9F%E8%8D%89%E9%9A%8A%29"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "SBDから改修更新する場合"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "これは未改造の九九式艦爆(江草隊)を彗星(江草隊)に改修更新するのとほぼ同等のコストになる*10", "links": [{"text": "九九式艦爆(江草隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B9%9D%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E7%88%86%28%E6%B1%9F%E8%8D%89%E9%9A%8A%29"}, {"text": "彗星(江草隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%BD%97%E6%98%9F%28%E6%B1%9F%E8%8D%89%E9%9A%8A%29"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "SBDから改修更新する場合"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "図鑑埋め以外では、艦爆として汎用性が高いうえに最強クラスのあちらを優先した方が良いだろう。", "links": [{"text": "九九式艦爆(江草隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B9%9D%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E7%88%86%28%E6%B1%9F%E8%8D%89%E9%9A%8A%29"}, {"text": "彗星(江草隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%BD%97%E6%98%9F%28%E6%B1%9F%E8%8D%89%E9%9A%8A%29"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "SBDから改修更新する場合"}, {"types": ["improvement", "ship"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "彗星(江草隊)の場合、必要数がさらに多い代わりに初期装備として入手が容易な物だけで済む*11", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "SBDから改修更新する場合"}, {"types": ["improvement", "development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "上述の通り、必要な装備等も多種多量な上に開発以外で入手困難な物もあり、消費資源も重い*12", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "SBDから改修更新する場合"}, {"types": ["improvement", "development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "運が悪いと、SBDや32型等必要装備の開発でさらに大量の資源と開発資材が飛んでいくことに…。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "SBDから改修更新する場合"}, {"types": ["ship", "development"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "Hornet改の初期装備としてそれぞれ★+4のSBDとF4F-4を入手可能。\nこれらを改修元にする場合、SBD→SBD-5は開発資材12個と改修資材8個、F4F-4→F6F-3は両資材12個分軽くなる。", "links": [{"text": "Hornet改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Hornet%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "SBD-5", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/SBD-5"}, {"text": "改修", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%A8#id195"}, {"text": "Saratoga改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Saratoga%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "Intrepid", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Intrepid"}, {"text": "F6F-5", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F6F-5"}, {"text": "改修", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%A8#id277"}, {"text": "任", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F61"}, {"text": "務", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F63"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "持参装備を利用する場合", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "Hornet改", "shipId": 704, "shipName": "Hornet改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 704, "canonicalShipName": "Hornet改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 704, "shipName": "Hornet改", "apiSortno": 1704, "apiAftershipId": 0}, "linkTarget": "Hornet改", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Hornet%E6%94%B9"}, {"rawName": "Saratoga改", "shipId": 438, "shipName": "Saratoga改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 438, "canonicalShipName": "Saratoga改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 438, "shipName": "Saratoga改", "apiSortno": 238, "apiAftershipId": 545}, "linkTarget": "Saratoga改", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Saratoga%E6%94%B9"}, {"rawName": "Intrepid", "shipId": 549, "shipName": "Intrepid", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 549, "canonicalShipName": "Intrepid", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 549, "shipName": "Intrepid", "apiSortno": 349, "apiAftershipId": 397}, "linkTarget": "Intrepid", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Intrepid"}]}, {"types": ["ship"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "どのみちSBD-5の改修には、二番艦にHornet改が必要。", "links": [{"text": "改修", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%A8#id195"}, {"text": "Saratoga改", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Saratoga%E6%94%B9"}, {"text": "Intrepid", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Intrepid"}, {"text": "F6F-5", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/F6F-5"}, {"text": "改修", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%94%B9%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%A8#id277"}, {"text": "任", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F61"}, {"text": "務", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F63"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item", "context": "持参装備を利用する場合", "shipReferences": [{"rawName": "Saratoga改", "shipId": 438, "shipName": "Saratoga改", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 438, "canonicalShipName": "Saratoga改", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 438, "shipName": "Saratoga改", "apiSortno": 238, "apiAftershipId": 545}, "linkTarget": "Saratoga改", "linkHref": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/Saratoga%E6%94%B9"}, {"rawName": "Intrepid", "shipId": 549, "shipName": "Intrepid", "status": "resolved", "resolution": "start2-name", "evidence": "link-text", "canonicalShipId": 549, "canonicalShipName": "Intrepid", "start2Ship": {"shipId": 549, "shipName": "Intrepid", "apiSortno": 349, "apiAftershipId": 397}, "linkTarget": "Intrepid", "lin