{"equipmentId": 445, "equipmentName": "二式複戦 屠龍", "source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%E8%A4%87%E6%88%A6%20%E5%B1%A0%E9%BE%8D", "pageEquipmentId": 445, "sectionHeading": "入手方法について", "evidenceScope": "acquisition-section", "developmentAvailable": true, "developmentResolution": {"status": "resolved", "method": "wikiwiki-equipment-infobox-notes", "marker": "開発可", "rawText": "開発可(特殊)、改修可、入手方法基地航空隊にのみ装備可能"}, "currentMethodTypes": ["development"], "historicalMethodTypes": [], "methods": [{"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "2021年12月10日実装時点での入手方法は開発のみ。", "links": [{"text": "あきつ丸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E3%81%82%E3%81%8D%E3%81%A4%E4%B8%B8"}, {"text": "神州丸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%A5%9E%E5%B7%9E%E4%B8%B8"}, {"text": "宗谷(特務艦のみ)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%AE%97%E8%B0%B7"}, {"text": "山汐丸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%B1%B1%E6%B1%90%E4%B8%B8"}, {"text": "流星", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B5%81%E6%98%9F"}, {"text": "零式艦戦32型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A632%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "該当ページ", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BA#m72817ef"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "開発秘書艦はあきつ丸、神州丸、宗谷(特務艦のみ)、山汐丸。", "links": [{"text": "あきつ丸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E3%81%82%E3%81%8D%E3%81%A4%E4%B8%B8"}, {"text": "神州丸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%A5%9E%E5%B7%9E%E4%B8%B8"}, {"text": "宗谷(特務艦のみ)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%AE%97%E8%B0%B7"}, {"text": "山汐丸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%B1%B1%E6%B1%90%E4%B8%B8"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "開発率自体はボーキテーブルで山汐丸以外は12%、山汐丸は4%。", "links": [{"text": "山汐丸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%B1%B1%E6%B1%90%E4%B8%B8"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "本装備のみが狙いなら山汐丸以外とするのが良い。", "links": [{"text": "山汐丸", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%B1%B1%E6%B1%90%E4%B8%B8"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "流星・零式艦戦32型を除くホロ艦載機との同時狙いは不可能なため注意。", "links": [{"text": "流星", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B5%81%E6%98%9F"}, {"text": "零式艦戦32型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A632%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "該当ページ", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BA#m72817ef"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "詳細は開発の該当ページを参照。", "links": [{"text": "流星", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B5%81%E6%98%9F"}, {"text": "零式艦戦32型", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A632%E5%9E%8B"}, {"text": "該当ページ", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BA#m72817ef"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}], "methodCount": 6, "unclassifiedEvidenceCount": 0, "issueCount": 0, "accepted": true, "coverageStatus": "parsed", "schemaVersion": 3, "resolvedShipIds": [], "resolvedQuestKeys": [], "referenceIssueCount": 0, "referenceSchemaVersion": 2, "rawEvidence": {"cacheKey": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%E8%A4%87%E6%88%A6%20%E5%B1%A0%E9%BE%8D.html", "rawPath": ".spider/local/source-cache/wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%E8%A4%87%E6%88%A6%20%E5%B1%A0%E9%BE%8D.html", "contentSha256": "3bfe592546a13a99355d3f330b5b362947a0816167f4fe81fecbb2dbe3b15aac", "fetchedAt": 1783526039, "validatedAt": 1783526039, "acquisitionSource": "external-browser-session-crawl"}, "fetchAttempts": [{"candidateSource": "raw-cache", "status": "ok", "url": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%E8%A4%87%E6%88%A6%20%E5%B1%A0%E9%BE%8D", "cachePath": "wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BA%8C%E5%BC%8F%