個を超える追加要求数が発生する点には注意。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "更新改修の場合はもちろん改修資材が必要となる。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "改修による改修資材要求数は★5→★6以降の確実化を行うことで47個。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "更新改修の場合は地味に新型航空兵装資材1つと熟練搭乗員が2つ必要。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "熟練提督ほど余っていると思われるアイテムとはいえ、量産する場合十中八九流星改(友永隊)のためと思われ、天山友永→流星友永の更新時に搭乗員3がさらに必要なので搭乗員の枯渇にも注意。", "links": [], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["development", "ship", "improvement"], "availability": "current", "rawText": "飛龍改三牧場の最大の利点は流星改(友永隊)作成のベースとなる天山一二型(友永隊)も入手可能な点である。", "links": [{"text": "流星改(友永隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B5%81%E6%98%9F%E6%94%B9%28%E5%8F%8B%E6%B0%B8%E9%9A%8A%29"}, {"text": "天山一二型(友永隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%A4%A9%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%8C%E5%9E%8B%28%E5%8F%8B%E6%B0%B8%E9%9A%8A%29"}, {"text": "九七式艦攻(友永隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%94%BB%28%E5%8F%8B%E6%B0%B8%E9%9A%8A%29"}, {"text": "紫電改四", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%B4%AB%E9%9B%BB%E6%94%B9%E5%9B%9B"}, {"text": "飛龍改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%A3%9B%E9%BE%8D%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "零式艦戦21型(熟練)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B%28%E7%86%9F%E7%B7%B4%29"}, {"text": "経験値", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E7%B5%8C%E9%A8%93%E5%80%A4#o54fc4a2"}, {"text": "牧場対象", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/22%E5%8F%B7%E5%AF%BE%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E6%8E%A2%E6%94%B9%E5%9B%9B"}, {"text": "鳥海改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%B3%A5%E6%B5%B7%E6%94%B9%E4%