"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "飛龍改二では更新不可。", "links": [{"text": "飛龍改二", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%A3%9B%E9%BE%8D%E6%94%B9%E4%BA%8C"}, {"text": "改三", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%A3%9B%E9%BE%8D%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%89"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "理論上は一応量産も可能だが、天山一二型(友永隊)の後半の改修に必要な天山一二型甲合計4つ、及び更新に必要な流星改(熟練)が2つ。", "links": [{"text": "天山一二型(友永隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%A4%A9%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%8C%E5%9E%8B%28%E5%8F%8B%E6%B0%B8%E9%9A%8A%29"}, {"text": "天山一二型甲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%A4%A9%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%8C%E5%9E%8B%E7%94%B2"}, {"text": "流星改(熟練)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B5%81%E6%98%9F%E6%94%B9%28%E7%86%9F%E7%B7%B4%29"}, {"text": "飛龍改三", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%A3%9B%E9%BE%8D%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%89"}, {"text": "九七式艦攻(友永隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%94%BB%28%E5%8F%8B%E6%B0%B8%E9%9A%8A%29"}, {"text": "機種転換", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99#id-F13"}], "evidenceKind": "list-item"}, {"types": ["improvement"], "availability": "current-or-summary", "rawText": "これらを作るコストも含めると、本装備を1つ作るだけでも大量の装備やアイテムが必要となり、かなり大変。", "links": [{"text": "天山一二型(友永隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%A4%A9%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%8C%E5%9E%8B%28%E5%8F%8B%E6%B0%B8%E9%9A%8A%29"}, {"text": "天山一二型甲", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E5%A4%A9%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%8C%E5%9E%8B%E7%94%B2"}, {"text": "流星改(熟練)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E6%B5%81%E6%98%9F%E6%94%B9%28%E7%86%9F%E7%B7%B4%29"}, {"text": "飛龍改三", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%A3%9B%E9%BE%8D%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%89"}, {"text": "九七式艦攻(友永隊)", "href": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%83%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%94%BB%28%E5%8F%8B%E6%B0%B8%E9%9A%8A%29"}, {"text": "機種転換", "